\id ACT  
\h Acts 
\toc1 Solchah Ho Pathen Natoh 
\toc2 Acts 
\toc3 Act 
\mt1 ACTS  
\mt2 SOLCHAHHO PATHEN NATOH  
\mt3 Mijouse dinga Kipana Thupha  
\is1 Acts lekhabu sung thu umdan  
\ip Jesu Christan athi nungin jong houbung masaho hinkhoa kon'in natoh anajom nalaiyin chule tukhang jengin jong amite mangchan na atong jing nalaiyin ahi. Solchah ho natoh lekhabu hi Lhagao Theng thahatna jal'a seijui masahon Jesu thuhil anabanjop nau thusim ahi. Hiche thusim hi eiho dinga kitilkhouna ahin, hichun houbung hi hahsatna tamtah um jongleh Pathen'in apuihoi jing ding ahi tichu eihilun ahi. Houbung kikhelna, khantouna, chule halna hi mihem natoh vang hilouva Lhagao Theng panhu navanga joh ahi tijong eihilun ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu jihpa chule akijih kum  
\ip Hiche lekhabu hi Luke in ajih ahin, AD 63-70 kikah sunga anajih ahi.  
\is1 Koiho dinga kijih ham?  
\ip Thusim jihthem khat hinan, Luke in hiche lekhabu hi Theophilus (Pathen ngailupa) henga Jesu Christa thodoh jouva thilsoh ho anasut ahi. Luke in kidangtah a houbung khantou thu le, thunei vaihom ho henga houbung thudol hilchetna, ahilou le seijui masaho tahsan thudol ahilchetna lekhabu ahi. Chujongleh Luke in Lhagao Theng in Juda te le Chidang Namdang te kikah a kihetkhelna asuhbeina thusim jong asei nom ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Luke thuphondoh  
\p
\v 1 Theophilus, ka lekhabu masa-a kahin sei chu, Jesu thilbol le thuhil kipattil thudol jouse le\x + \xo 1:1 \xt Lk 1:1-4\x*  
\v 2 Lhagao Thenga konna alhendoh solchah ho thu apeh jouva pat ama van'a lahtouva aum ni gei thu ahi.   
\s1 Jesu van a akaltou  
\p
\v 3 Chuche thingpel chunga athia athodoh jou nisomli sung chun, ama solchah ho henga akilah jin, chule ama ahing monge ti chu photchetna tamtah avetsah jin, chuleh Pathen Lenggam thudol aseiyin ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin solchah ho toh anehkhom laiyin, aman amaho chu thu apen, “Kana seipeh bangun Pan akitepna thilpeh ahinsol masangsen nang hon Jerusalem dalha hih un.\x + \xo 1:4 \xt Lk 24:49\x*  
\v 5 John in twiya baptize na chansah u ahin, ahin tu apat nikho phabep jou le nangho Lhagao Thenga baptize nachan ding'u ahi.” ati.\x + \xo 1:5 \xt Matt 3:11; Mk 1:8; Lk 3:16; Jn 1:33\x*  
\v 6 Hichun solchah ho chu Jesu toh aumkhom pet un, ama hon adongun, “Pakai, Israel te chamlhatna ding leh alenggam nakiledoh sah kitna ding phat chu hitam?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Aman adonbut in, “Anikho leh aphat chu Pa changseh thaneina a um ahin, nangho hetding dol ahipoi.  
\v 8 Ahinlah Lhagao Theng nachung uva ahung chuh tengleh nang hon thahatna nanei ding'u ahi. Chutengleh nangho Jerusalem'a, Judea gam'a, Samaria gam, leh leiset chung pumpia kathu hettohsah a napan ding'u ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 1:8 \xt Matt 28:19; Mk 16:15; Lk 24:47,48\x*  
\v 9 Thu hicheng chu asei jouvin, ama hon avet jing laiyun ama chu meiloma lahtouvin aumin ahileh ama hon amupha tapouvin ahi.\x + \xo 1:9 \xt Mk 16:19; Lk 24:50,51\x*  
\v 10 Chutia ama hon van lam'a lahtouva aumpet avet jing laiyun pon-banga kivon mini alah uvah ahung ding lhonin,  
\v 11 “Galilee mite, ibola nadin uva vanlam navet jingu ham? Jesu nangho kom'a konna van'a lahtouva aum banga hi nikhat le vanna konna hung kile kit ding ahi!” ati lhon'e.   
\s1 Judas khel'a seijui khat kilheng  
\p
\v 12 Chuin solchah ho chu Jerusalem'a konna mile keh a gamla Olive mola kon chun Jerusalem'ah ahung kile tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Jerusalem ahung lhunun aumnau inchung langah akal touvun ahi. Amaho chu: Peter, John, Jacob, Andrew, Philip, Thomas, Bartholomew, Matthew, Jacob (Alphaeus chapa), Simon (Zealot), chule Judas (Jacob chapa), ahiuve.\x + \xo 1:13 \xt Matt 10:2-4; Mk 3:16-19; Lk 6:14-16\x*  
\v 14 Amaho chengse hi Jesu nu Mary leh numei dang phabep toh, Jesu sopite phabep toh akikhomun gunchu leh lungkhat tah in atao jom jing tauve.   
\s1 Matthias in Judas akhel  
\p
\v 15 Jesu tahsan mipi jakhat le somni akikhop khom laitah uvin Peter adingdoh in,  
\v 16 “Sopi te ho, Jesu manho lamkaiya pang Judas thudol hi, kum sottah masanga Lhagao Thengin Leng David kam'a ana phondohsa Pathen Lekhabua thu chu guilhungah ahi.  
\v 17 Ijeh-inem itileh Judas chu eiho lah a khat ahin, hiche lhacha hina jong hi changah ahi,” ati.  
\v 18 (Aman khan gitlou man sumin gambeh khat achon, akhupboh in achun atumpi apohkeh in agil jouse ahung dohtan ahi.\x + \xo 1:18 \xt Matt 27:3-8\x*  
\v 19 Judas thi thu hi Jerusalem mite jouse kom'a ahung kithangsoh tan ahileh ama hon hiche gambeh chu Aramaic paovin Akeldama asah tauvin, hichu Thisan Gambeh tina ahi.)  
\v 20 Peter in aseijom kit in, “Psalm lekhabua kimu bangin ‘Ama In chu onghen, koima cheng hihhen, chuleh ama panmun chu midang khat changhen,’ ati.\x + \xo 1:20 \xt Labu 69:25; \xt Labu 109:8\x*  
\v 21 Hijeh a chu Judas panmun khel ding mikhat ilhen ding'u ahin ama chu Pakai Jesu toh iumkhom lai uva pat a eiho lah a um jing khat hi ding.\x + \xo 1:21 \xt Matt 3:16; Mk 1:9; Lk 3:21; \xt Mk 16:19; Lk 24:51\x*  
\v 22 John'in baptize achansah jouva pat eiho lah a konna Jesu lahtouva aumni geiya eiho lah a lhajing hi ding, ama chu Jesu thodoh thudol hettohsah dinga eiho lah a pang ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 23 Chuin mini: Barsabbas kiti Joseph (Justus tia jong kihe) le Matthias chu alhengdoh un,  
\v 24 Amaho ataovun, “Vo Pakai, nangma mijouse lungthim hesoh nahi,  
\v 25 Hiche teni hi koijoh in Judas khel'a solchah na atoh ding ham nei hetsah uvin, ajeh chu Judas chun hiche solchah natoh hi alhatan ahi.”  
\v 26 Chuin ama hon vang asangun ahileh Matthias chu solchah som le khat ho lah a akisimtha tan ahi.   
\ms1 Solchah ho Lhagao Thenga adimu  
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Pentecost nikho chun tahsan chate jouse chu munkhat a ana umkhomun ahi.\x + \xo 2:1 \xt Thempu Dan 23:15-21; Danbu Ni Na 16:9-11\x*  
\v 2 Chuin phulou helouvin van'a kon'in hui hattah gin tobang ahung ging in, atoukhom nau in chu ahung dimset jeng tan ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin meikong toh kilou ahilou le meikong banga kong lei ahung kilah in amaho jouse chunga chun achutan ahi.  
\v 4 chuin amaho jouse chu Lhagao Theng adimsoh tauvin ahileh Lhaogao Theng in apeh bangun ama hon paochom paochom in thu aseipan tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche pet a chu vannoi gamtin'a konna hungkhom Judah hougut ho jong Jerusalem'a um'u ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin chuche gin chu ajah phat un mipi ajapha jouse chu ahung khomun ahileh tahsan chate thusei chu ama ama pao cheh a ajah jeh uchun amaho alung kichih lahlah jengun ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin amaho chun kidang asauvin, “Hiche hi iti hithei ham?” tin adatmo lheh jengun ahi. “Hiche mite hi abonchauva Galilee mi ahiuvin,  
\v 8 ahinlah eihon eima eima penna gam cheh paovin ijauve!  
\v 9 Eiho hila Parthia mi, Mede mi, Elam mi ihiuvin, abang Mesopotamia gam'a cheng, Judah gam le Cappadocia gam'a cheng, Pontus gam'a le Asia gam'a cheng,  
\v 10 Phrygia le Pamphylia gam'a cheng, Egypt gam'a cheng chule Cyrene gam vel'a, Libya gam'a cheng ihiuvin; abang Rome a konna hung kholjin, Judah chona chonho,  
\v 11 chule Crete mi le Arab gam mi ihiuvin; ahivangin eima pao cheh a Pathen thilbol loupi thu aseiyu thakhat jah in ijauve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 12 Amaho chun kidang asauvin adatmo lheh jengun “Itidan ahidem,” tin khat le khat akidongto tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Ahivangin mipi lah a konkhat chun ajontaiyun, “Hite ho hi lengpitwi kham ahiuve,” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Mipi masanga Peter thusei  
\p
\v 14 Chuin Peter chu solchah dang som le khat chutoh adingdoh in mipi ho kom'a chun aw sangtah in asamin ajah uva, “Phatechan ngaiyuvin, Judah mite le Jerusalem'a cheng mite! Hiche thu hi nang hon hekhel hih un,  
\v 15 Nangho ngaito banga hite ho hi lengpitwi kham ahi pouve, ajeh chu tuhi jingkah nidan ko ahinalai bouve.  
\v 16 Ahin hiche namu uhi Joel themgaopan ana phondohsa guilhunna ahi bouve:  
\v 17 ‘Pathen'in’ ninunung lam le hiti ding ahi, mijouse chunga Ka Lhagao kabuhlhah ding ahi. Na chapa teu le na chanu teuvin gaothu asei dingu, chule na khangdong ho'uvin mu aneiyuva, chule na Upa ho'uvin mang anei dingu ahi.\x + \xo 2:17 \xt Joel 2:28-32\x*  
\v 18 Hiche niteng chule kasoh pasalte le kasoh numeite chunga ka-Lhagao kabuhlhah ding ama hon gaothu asei dingu ahi.  
\v 19 chuleh van'a thil kidang tampi kasosah ding, leiset chunga melchihna tampi-thisan, meikong le meikhu kamusah ding ahi.  
\v 20 Pakai hungkitna nikho loupitah ahung lhun masanga, Nisa hung thim ding, lha jong thisan soh ding ahi.”  
\v 21 Ahinlah koi hijongleh Pakai min kou jouse sohcha ding ahi.  
\v 22 “Nangho Israel mite, ngaiyuvin! Pathen'in Nazareth Jesu chu nangho lah a amanchah a bolmo kidang, datmo umho, chule melchihna ho abola konna chu aphotchetsah ahin, hichu nang hon nahet u ahi.  
\v 23 Ahin Pathen'in ahet masat le agontoh masat bangin Jesu chu pehdoh in aum tan ahileh nang hon dan neilou chidang namdang te toh kithon thingpel a nakhenbeh un nathat tauvin ahi.”\x + \xo 2:23 \xt Matt 27:35; Mk 15:24; Lk 23:33; Jn 19:18\x*  
\v 24 Ahin Pathen'in Ama chu kichat umtah thina a kon'in alha-ong in hinna apekit tan ahi ajeh chu thina in atuhden hoi ahilou jeh chun.\x + \xo 2:24 \xt Matt 28:5,6; Mk 16:6; Lk 24:5\x*  
\v 25 Leng David in Ama thudol aseiyin, “Keiman Pakai chu kamaikoh a kamu jinge; keima kalonle louding ahi ajeh chu kajetlama ama aum jinge.\x + \xo 2:25 \xt Labu 16:8-11\x*  
\v 26 Hijeh chun kalung akipah in, chule kalei athanome; chuche kalval chun katahsa jong kinem'a cholnga ding ahi;  
\v 27 Ajeh chu nangman kalhagao mithiho lah a na dalhah louding, namitheng monmangna namusah louding ahi.  
\v 28 Nangman keima hinna lampi neihetsah ahitan, namaisoa kipana neidip ding ahi, ati.”  
\v 29 “Sopi te ho, hiche thu hi ngaito temuvin, Ipu-u David in ama chung chang thu asei ahilou dan kicheh tah in iheuve, ajeh chu ama athi in, akivuina lhanmun jeng jong tugeiyin eiholah a aumin ahi.  
\v 30 Ahin ama themgao ahijeh chun, Pathen'in Ama taiguiya pengkhat alaltouna a atousah ding, kihahsela athutep chu ahen,\x + \xo 2:30 \xt Labu 132:11; 2 Samuel 7:12,13\x*  
\v 31 Chutia chu khonung thu ahet masah jeh chun Messiah thokit thu aseiyin, ‘Thikhol khul'ah dalhah denin aumpoi, alongin jong monmangna amupoi,’ ati.  
\v 32 Pathen'in Jesu chu thina a kon'in akaithouvin, keiho jouse hi ahettoh kahiuve.  
\v 33 Tun Ama van'a Pathen khut jetlama choisangin aumin, athutepsa Lhagao Theng chu a-Pa a kon'in amun, hichu ahin bunglhan, tua namu u najah uhi ahi.  
\v 34 David chu ama tah van'a akaltou lou vangin hitin aseiye, ‘Pakai chun ka Pakai jah a, jabolna mun kakhut jetlam'a tou jingin,\x + \xo 2:34 \xt Labu 110:1\x*  
\v 35 Namelma te kasuhnem a, nakeng chotpha a kaneisah masang sen,’ ati.  
\v 36 Chuti ahijeh chun Israel chate jousen heuvin, Pathen'in hiche Jesu, thingpel chunga na khetbeh pau chu Pakai le Messiah dinga atundoh ahitai!”   
\s1 Mi sangthum in tahsanna nei  
\p
\v 37 Peter thusei chun alungthim'u asuntan ahile ama hon Peter le seijui dang ho kom'a chun, “Sopi te ho keihon ipi kabol dingu ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 38 Peter in adonbut in, “Na chonset lungheiyun lang Pathen lama hung kiheiyun, chule na chonset nau ngaidama aum jeh in Jesu Christa minin twiya baptize changun, chutengleh Lhagao Theng thilpeh nachan dingu ahi.  
\v 39 Hiche thutep hi nangho le nachateu ding, chule chidang namdang te ding le, Pakai Pathen'in akou mite jouse dinga jong ahi,” ati.  
\v 40 Chule Peter in thu tampi asei jomjing nalaiyin, amaho chu atilkhouvin, “Hiche khang gilou mite a kon hin kihuhdoh un,” atin ahi.  
\v 41 Hiche nikho a Peter thusei tahsanho jouse chu twija baptize achangun, hiche nikho chun Houbung mi sangthum ana kibe in ahi.   
\s1 Solchah ho melchihna natoh kidang ho  
\p
\v 42 Tahsan chate jouse chun solchah ho thuhil jong, kiloikhomna jong, neh leh chah kihopkhomna le Pakai anjon a jong, taokhomna a jong gunchu tah in ana pangdet jingun ahi.  
\v 43 Chuin alungthim sung uva kichatna nasatah ahung lhungin, solchah hon jong melchihna le thil kidang tamtah abol tauve.  
\v 44 chuin tahsan chate jouse chu munkhat ah aumkhom un athilnei jouseu chu neilhaangin ana neikhom uvin ahi.\x + \xo 2:44 \xt Act 4:32-35\x*  
\v 45 Anei agou u ajoh uvin asum chu angaicha jouse toh ana kihom jiuvin ahi.  
\v 46 Niseh in Hou-Ina Pathen ahoukhom jiuvin, Pakai anjon jong dingin in'ah akikhom jiuvin, chule kipah tah le hongphal tah in an ana nekhom jiuvin ahi.  
\v 47 Abonchauva Pathen avahchoi jing laiyu le mijouse lungdeiya thanom tah a aum jing laiyun, aniseh in Pathen'in huhhing'a um ho chu amaho lah a chun abe jing tan ahi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Elbai khat suhdam a um  
\p
\v 1 Nikhat Peter le John chu nilhah lang taokhom phat in, hichu nidan thum don ahin, Hou-In'ah achelhonin ahi.  
\v 2 Hou-In ahung nai lhontah chun apen a pat a elbai mikhat ahin polut un, ama pa chun Hou-In'a cheho jouse kom'a akithum theina dinga niseh le Hou-In Kotkha Hoi atiu mun'a chu akoi jiu ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche mipa chun Hou-In'a lut kigo Peter le John amu phat chun sum themkhat neipe lhonin tin athum tan ahi.  
\v 4 Peter le John in amapa chu ave changmel lhonin, hichun Peter in amapa kom'a chun, “Neive lhonin” ati.  
\v 5 Hichun elbaipa chun sum themkhat beh mu ding kinem in amani chu lunglut tah in avelhon tan ahi.  
\v 6 Ahin Peter in “Nang dingin Dangka le Sana kanei poi, ahinlah kaneisun penge, Nazareth Jesu Christa minin dingin lang lam jot in.” ati.  
\v 7 Chuin Peter in elbaipa chu akhut jet in atuh in akithopi in akai ding tan ahileh, mipa kengphang le a ahkhomit chu apettah chun adamtan chule athahatdoh tan ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin akichomin akengphang in adingdoh in lam ajot pantan, amani chutoh Hou-In sunga alut in avahlen, akichomin, chule Pathen avahchoi tan ahi.  
\v 9 Mi jousen elbaipa lamjot chu amu uvin, Pathen avahchoi chu aja uvin ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin miho chun Hou-In Kotkha Hoi a touva khutdopa ahi chu ahetdoh phat un kidang asauvin adatmo lheh jeng'un ahi.  
\v 11 Hiche pa chun Peter le John atuhchah kheh laitah chun mipi jouse chun kidang asa behseh jeng uvin, Solomon Kempum atiuva chun ahung lhai khomun ahi.   
\s1 Mipi henga Peter thusei  
\p
\v 12 Peter in chutobang phat gomkom amutah chun mipi ho chu adonbut in, “Vo Israel mite,” hiche chung changa hi ipi kidang nasah uham? Ipi dinga keihon keiho thahat le houdih vanga hiche pa hi lam kajotsah dan uva na ngaito uva neivet vet jeng'u ham?  
\v 13 Ajeh chu Abraham, Isaac le Jacob Pathen, ipu ipateu Pathen chun alhacha Jesu choiatna dinga hiche hi abol ahi. Hiche Jesu chu nang hon napam paiyun, Pilate in lhadoh dinga agotlai in jong nang hon ama khut ah napedoh un ahi.\x + \xo 3:13 \xt Potdohbu 3:15\x*  
\v 14 Nanghon hiche thengtah le chondihtah pa sangin, tolthatpa joh na lhadoh pehna dingun nathumun ahi.\x + \xo 3:14 \xt Matt 27:15-23; Mk 15:6-14; Lk 23:13-23; Jn 19:12-15\x*  
\v 15 Nang hon hinna bulpi chu nathat un, ahin Pathen'in thina a kon'in akaithou kittan, chule keiho hi hiche thutah hetoh chu kahiuve!  
\v 16 Jesu min'a tahsan vanga hiche pa hi damah ahin, chule tumasanga iti dammo ham jong nahet u ahi. Jesu min'a tahsanna chun namitmu tah uva adamsah ahi.  
\v 17 Sopi te ho, nangho le navaipo teuvin Jesu nabol nau hi hetlouva nabol'u ahi kahenai.  
\v 18 Ajeh chu Messiah thohgim ding thudol, themgao hon ana sei masahsa chu Pathen'in aguilhun sah ahi.  
\v 19 Tun na chonset lung heiyun lang Pathen lama hung kile hei kit un, chutileh na chonset nau thehngima um ding,  
\v 20 Pakai angsunga konna kiledohna phat hunglhung thei kit a, chutengleh nangho dinga agotsa Jesu Christa chu naheng uva ahinsol kit ding ahi.  
\v 21 Ajeh chu Pathen'in phatsot apat a Themgao thengho ana seidoh sah akitepna banga, ama chu thil jouse akiledoh sah kit phat hung kah a van'a umden ding ahi.  
\v 22 Mose’n “Pakai Pathen'in keima eitundoh banga hi nangho dinga nasopi teu lah a khat themgaova atundoh ding ahi; ama chun najah uva thu asei jouse chu nangai dingu ahi.\x + \xo 3:22 \xt Danbu Ni Na 18:15,18\x*  
\v 23 Chule koi hijongleh chuche themgao thusei ngailou chu Pathen mite lah a konna kisumanghel ding ahi,” anati.\x + \xo 3:23 \xt Danbu Ni Na 18:19\x*  
\v 24 “Samuel khanga pat themgao jousen tukhanga thilsoh umchan jouse ana seiyun ahi.  
\v 25 Nangho chuche themgao ho leh Pathen'in naputeu napa teu atepna thutep chate chu nahiu ahi; ajeh chu Pathen'in Abraham kom'a chu nangma chilhah a konna vannoi leiset phung jouse phatthei chang ding ahi, tia ana tepsa ahi.\x + \xo 3:25 \xt Semtilbu 22:18\x*  
\v 26 Pathen'in alhacha Jesu akaithou kit jou chun, na chonset nau lampia konna nahung kilekitna ding ule phatthei nachan theina ding uva nangho Israel mite henga ahinsol masatpen ahi,” ati.   
\c 4  
\s1 Lamkai ho kikhopna a Peter le John  
\p
\v 1 Peter le John in mipi ho henga thu asei jing lai lhonin, Thempu ho le Hou-In vengbit a pang vaipo, chuleh Sadducee ho themkhat chun lungphamo tah in ahung kimaitopi uvin,  
\v 2 Peter le John in Jesu vanga thokitna aum'e tithu ahil lhon jeh chun hiche lamkai ho chu alung phamo lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin amani chu amanun, nilhah lam ahiphat in ajing khovah kah chun songkul'a akhum tauvin ahi.  
\v 4 Ahin athuhil lhon jaho lah a mi tamtah chun athuhil lhon chu atahsan tauvin ahileh numei chapang simlouvin tahsan mi sangnga aval tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Chuin ajing nikho chun, avaipoteu le a upateu chule danthu sunho chu Jerusalem'a akikhomun ahi.  
\v 6 Ama ho lah a chun Annas Thempu Chungnung jaonan Caiaphas, John, Alexander, chuleh Thempu Chungnung insung mite dang jong aumun ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin amaho angsunga chun solchah teni chu ahin puilut un thudoh aneiyun, “Ipi thaneina, ahilouleh koi min'a hitobang thil hi nabol lhon ham?” tin adongun ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin Lhagao Theng dimset pumin Peter chun adonbut un, “Vaipo ho leh Upate ho,  
\v 9 Elbaipa chunga thilpha kabol jeh lhona thudoh neibol'u ham? Elbaipa hi iti dam ham nahet chet nomu ham?  
\v 10 Nangho le Israel chate jouse dingin kicheh tah in naseipeh uving kate, nanghon thingpel chunga nakhetbeh uva ahivanga Pathen'in thina a konna akaithoukit, thaneitah Nazareth Jesu Christa min'a dama ahi.  
\v 11 Ajeh chu Jesu thudol'a Pathen Lekhabun hiti hin aseiyin ahi, nangho insahon nadeimo uva napaiyu song aninga apipena panga chu ama hi ahi.\x + \xo 4:11 \xt Labu 118:22\x*  
\v 12 Chule koima danga huhhingna aumpoi, vannoiya huhhing'a iumna diu min dang amin dang Pathen'in eipe pouve,” ati  
\v 13 Chuin vaipo ho chun Peter le John hansanna chu amu uvin adatmo lheh jengun ahi. Ajeh chu lekha themlou le jilna neimi ahi lhon lou chu aheuvin chule Jesu to ana umkhom ahi lhon jong aheuvin ahi.  
\v 14 Ahin akiboldam mipa alailungtah uva adin amujeh u chun, vaipo ho chun seibe ding ahe tapouvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin kikhop khomna in'a konna potdoh dingin Peter le John chu thu apeuvin, chuin amaho le amaho chu akihouvun,  
\v 16 “Hiche miteni hi i-ilo dingu ham? Thil bolmo kidang abol lhon la inelthei pouvin, chule Jerusalem'a mijousen jong ahen,  
\v 17 Ahin Jesu min'a thu ahiljomkit lhon louna dingin gihsalna neiyu hite,” akitiuvin ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin Solchah teni akoulut kit un, Jesu min'a thu ahilkit lhon louna dingin thu apeuvin ahi.  
\v 19 Ahin Peter le John in adonbut lhonin, “Pathen thu ngailouva nangho thujoh kangai diu chu Pathen'in deijonte tia nagel uham?  
\v 20 Kamu jouseu le kajah jouseu sapphong ding hi kangah thei lhon louding ahi,” ati lhonin ahi.  
\v 21 Chuin ama hon agihsal kit un achainan alhadoh tauvin ahi, ajeh chu mipi tamtah jeh a chu asuhgim theilou u ahi. Mijousen Pathen avahchoiyun ahi.  
\v 22 Ajeh chu kum somli elbaipa kiboldamna chu bolmo thil kidangtah ahi.   
\s1 Hansanna dinga Jesu tahsan ho atao u  
\p
\v 23 Chuin alhadoh jou jouvun, Peter le John chu tahsan chate kom'a ahung kile lhonin thempu ho leh upate hon asei jouseu chu asei lhon tan ahileh.  
\v 24 Akom uva Peter le John thusei ajah jah u chun tahsan chate jouse chun okhat tah in Pathen kom'a hiti hin atao tauvin ahi. “Vo thaneipen Pakai, Van le leiset, twikhanglen le asunga thil um jouse hinsempa,\x + \xo 4:24 \xt Potdohbu 20:11; Nehemiah 9:6; Labu 146:6\x*  
\v 25 Nangin Lhagao Thenga kapuluiyu nalhacha David kam'a ‘Namtin vaipi ibola lunghanga hiuvem? Chule ibola mihon mohthil angaitou ham?\x + \xo 4:25 \xt Labu 2:1,2\x*  
\v 26 Leiset chunga a lengteu galsat din akigong chaiyun, a Pakai le a Christa dou dingin avaipoteu akikhomui’ tia nasei sah ahin,  
\v 27 Atahbeh in hiche khopi sunga hin alhungtai! Ajeh chu Herod Antipas, gamvaipo Pontius Pilate, chidang namdang te le Israel chate jouse chu nangma thaonusa nalhacha theng Jesu dou dingin akitho khom sohkei tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 4:27 \xt Lk 23:7-11; \xt Matt 27:1,2; Mk 15:1; Lk 23:1; Jn 18:28,29\x*  
\v 28 Ahinlah abol jouseu hi nangma lungcham tah a bol dinga umsa ahi.  
\v 29 Chuleh tun O Pakai, amigihsal nau hi ngaiyin lang na lhachate hin nathu kasap phongna diuvin hansanna lentah chu neipeuvin.  
\v 30 Na midamsah theina thahat toh thon nakhut hinlhaang inlang, nalhacha theng Jesu minin melchihna le bolmo kidang dang bol uhen” atiuve.  
\v 31 Hitia atao jouvun, akikhop nau in chu ahung kilingin, abonchauvin Lhagao Theng adimset un, hangsan tah in Pathen thu alhangsamun ahi.   
\s1 Tahsan chaten thil anei khom u  
\p
\v 32 Chuin tahsan chate jouse chu lungkhat le thakhat ahiuvin, koiman jong anei chu keiya tum ahi tilouvin, anei jouseu abonchan aneikhomun ahi.\x + \xo 4:32 \xt Act 2:44,45\x*  
\v 33 Solchah ho chun thaneitah in Pakai Jesu thokit thudol chu a hettohsah jiuvin, chule Pathen phatthei bohna lentah chu amaho chunga aum tan ahi.  
\v 34 Amaho lah a chun alhasam angaicha anaum pouvin ahi ajeh chu gam leiset le in neihon ahinjoh un,  
\v 35 asum chu solchah ho kengbul'a ahin choiyun alhasam angaicha ho chu anahop peh jiuvin ahi.  
\v 36 Chuin Joseph, solchah hon Barnabas asah u (hichu lungmon konna chapa tina ahi) chu Levi phungmi Cyprus twikol gam mi ahi.  
\v 37 Amapa chun lou munkhat anei chu ahinjoh in asum chu solchahte kengbul'a ahin choiyin ahi.   
\ms1 Ananias le Sapphira  
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Ahin Ananias kiti mipa khat ana um'in ama chun ajinu Sapphira to agou themkhat ajoh lhonin,  
\v 2 Asum kehkhat chu solchah ho henga ahin choi lhonin, abona kahin choi lhon ahitai ati lhonin adangse chu ajinu toh kinopto in akikoi den lhon tan ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Peter chun aseiyin, “Ananias ipi dinga nalungthim chu Satan nalodimsah hitam? Lhagao Theng najoulhep in nasum akehkhat nanga dingin nakikoi tai.  
\v 4 Nagouthil chu nanga ahi, joh ding le joh louding jong nangma thu ahi, najoh jouva jong asum chu nanga ahin, pehdoh ding le pehdoh louding jong nangma thu ahi. Ipi dinga hitobang hi nabol hitam? Hiche hi keiho nei joubol nau ahipon Pathen najou bolna joh ahi” ati.  
\v 5 Hiche thu chu Ananias in ajah jah chun lhonglaiya chun alhun athitai, chuin hiche thu ajapha jouse chu akicha thei lheh tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin khangdong phabep ahungdoh un ponin atomun vui dingin apodoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 7 Nidan thum vel che jouvin, thilsoh imacha hepha louvin ajinu chu ahungin,  
\v 8 Chuin Peter in adongin, “Hiche sum hi najipa toh nagam mana namu lhon chu hitam?” atileh amanun jong “Henge hichu kagam man lhon ahi,” ati.  
\v 9 Chuin Peter in aseiyin, “Ipi dinga nani tah lhon'a Pakai Lhagao napatep lhona hitobang thil phalou hi nabol lhon hitam? Najipa vuiya che gollhang hon kotphung ahinpha tauvin ahi, chule nang jong naputdoh diu ahitai,” ati.  
\v 10 Apettah chun lhonglaiya chun alhun athipai tan ahi. Gollhang ho ahunglut un ahileh amanu athisa anaum chu amu uvin chuin apodoh paiyun ajipa kivuina kom'a chun aga vui tauvin ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin Houbung pumpi le athu japha jouse chunga kichatna lentah achutan ahi.   
\s1 Solchah hon melchihna thil tampi abol'u  
\p
\v 12 Chuin solchah ho chun miholah a chun melchihna le thil kidang tampi abolun, tahsan chate jouse Hou-In a, Solomon kempum kiti mun'a chun niseh in akikhom jing tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Ahin mipi hon amaho chu amusang lheh vangun alah uva jaoding chu angam pouvin ahi.  
\v 14 Hijeng jong le tahsan chate chu Pakai henga hung akibe jing jengun, numei le pasal akibe jingun ahi.  
\v 15 Solchah ho natoh jeh chun miho chun Peter avale kom le alebeh achung uva achuh khah na ding tin damlou ho jouse chu lamlen dunga ahin podoh uvin lupna le pheh chunga alupsah un ahi.  
\v 16 Jerusalem kimvela khopi hoa kon chun mipi ahung khomun damlou ho le lhagao boh vop ho ahin puiyun ahileh abonchauvin adam sohkei uvin ahi.   
\s1 Solchah ho chunga gimna lhung kit  
\p
\v 17 Chuin Thempu Chungnung leh aloite Sadducee ho chu thangset nan adimset un ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin solchah ho chu amanun songkul'a chun ahen tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Ahin janin Pakai Lhagao ahungin, akihennau songkul kot chu ahongdoh in solchah ho chu apuidoh in,  
\v 20 “Hou-In a cheuvin lang miho kom'a hiche hinna thu hi gaseipeh tauvin,” ati.  
\v 21 Chuin ajing khovah in solchah ho chu Hou-In'a alut un, Pakai Lhagaovin akom uva aseipeh bangun ahil tauvin ahi. Chuin Thempu Chungnung chu atohkhompi chengtoh ahungin, Israel te lah a a upahou le hou vaipoloi ho chu akou khomun, chuin solchah ho chu achungthu u kholchen dingin songkul'a kon'in aga puidoh sah un ahi.  
\v 22 Hou-In ngah a pang sottol leho chu songkul'a ahungun ahileh, songkul'a chun koima anaum tapon ahi, chuin amaho akile uvin houvaipo ho henga chun thil umchan chu aseiyun,  
\v 23 “Songkul kot chu kikhah detchet a angah ho chu apama ding ahiuvin, ahin songkul kot chu ahon uva ahile asunga chun koima ana umpon ahi!” atiuve.  
\v 24 Chuin Hou-In ngahho lah a lamkaipa le thempu pipuho chu alungboi lheh jengun, ipi khat ahungsoh tadem tin adatmo lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin mikhat ahungin kidang satah in, “Songkul'a nakhum u miho chu Hou-In'a ading uvin miho thu ahil uve,” ahung tin ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin Hou-In ngah a pang sepai lamkaipa leh asepai te chu acheuvin solchah ho chu aga manun, ahin ajokhat le mipi ho chun songin eisep unte tin boina sem louvin oltah in agabol'un ahi.  
\v 27 Chuin solchah ho chu hou vaipoloi angsunga ahin puilut un, amaho chu Thempu Chungnung in thu adongun,  
\v 28 “Hiche mipa min chun thu hilkit tahih un tia hakhama kakham nahilou uham? Ahinlah nathuhil'u Jerusalem nadip soh un hiche mipa thina chung changa hin keiho neimoso go uve,” atin ahi.\x + \xo 5:28 \xt Matt 27:25\x*  
\v 29 Ahin Peter le solchah ho chun adonbut un, “Keihon mihem thuneiho sanga Pathen thu kangai joh dingu ahi.  
\v 30 Ipu ipateu Pathen chun thingpel chunga na khaisang uva nathau Jesu chu thina a konna akaithou kit ahi.  
\v 31 Ahin ama chu Pathen'in Pakai leh Huhhingpu dinga achoisanga akhut jetlama atousah ahitai. Chule hiche hi Israel chate chonset lungheina ding le ngaidam channa dinga abol ahi.  
\v 32 Keiho hi hiche thudol hettohsah chu kahiuvin, chuleh athua nungho dinga Pathen'in apeh Lhagao Theng jong chu ahi,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 33 Chuin hiche kisei ajah phat un hou vaipoloi ho chu alunghang doh jah un tha ding lung agel tauvin ahi.  
\v 34 Ahin hou vaipoloi lah a mikhat, Pharisee mi amin Gamaliel, amapa chu hou danthu them le mijousen ajabol mikhat ahin, ading doh in miho chu chomkhat pam langa soldoh dingin thu apen ahi.  
\v 35 Chuin aman aloite henga chun aseiyin, “Nangho Israel mite, hite ho chunga bol ding nagot uhi chingtheiyun!  
\v 36 Tu masang chun Theudas kiti mikhat ana um'in, ama chu milen khat bangin ana um'in ahile mihem jali valin anung ana jui un ahi, ahin ama chu ana that un ahileh anungjui ho chu lamchom cheh a ana vah cheh gamun, abol atoh hou jouse imalou asohtan ahi.  
\v 37 Amapa jou chun hichu min kisut lai ahin, Galilee mi Judas kiti mikhat anaum kit in ama jong chun anungjui mitampi ana neiyin, ahin athat kit un ahile anungjui ho jouse chu ana kithecheh kit tauvin ahi.  
\v 38 Chuti ahijeh chun hiche mite hi ima lohih un, moh lha-ong uvin, ajeh chu ama hon angaito uva abolgot uhi amaho lungchama ahile chomkhat jou le hung mang pai ding ahi.  
\v 39 Ahin Pathen a konna ahileh na suhmang joulou dingu, nangho le nangho Pathen toh kidoubep nahilo dingu ahi!” ati.  
\v 40 Chuin ama thumop chun akilol tauvin, solchah ho chu akouvun ajep uvin, chujouvin Jesu min'a thu aseikit tahlouna dingun agihsalun alha tauvin ahi.  
\v 41 Chuin solchah ho chu hou vaipoloi angsunga kon chun apotdoh un, Jesu min'a suhgima aum jeh uchun akipah lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 42 chule aniseh in Hou-In le ainson tin'ah “Jesu chu Messiah ahi,” tichu ahil'un asamphong jom jingun ahi.   
\c 6  
\s1 Lhacha dinga mi sagi kilhen  
\p
\v 1 Ahin aniseh a atahsan akibe jing phat in alah uva phunnoina le kilunglhaito louna aumdoh tan, hichun Greek pao tho atahsan ho chun Hebrew pao tho atahsan hon niseh a neh le chah kihopna a meithaiho akhohsah pouve tin aphunnoi tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin solchah som le ni ho chun atahsan ho chu abonchauvin akoukhom uvin, “Keiho solchah ho hin Pathen thuhilna a phat kaman diu ahin neh le chah a hi kaboi louding dol u ahi.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun sopi te ho, nang hon jaumtah, lhagao le chihna a dim mi sagi lhengdoh uvin lang amaho chu neh leh chah a mo kapohsah dingu ahi.  
\v 4 Chutileh keiho solchah ho hin taona le Pathen thuhil'a phat kaman thei dingu ahi,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 5 Abonchauvin hiche lunggel chu pha asauvin chuin, Stephen (tahsanna le lhagaova dim mipa), Philip, Procorus, Nicanor, Timon, Parmenas, le Antioch mi Nicolas (Judah te tahsana sang masaloi) ho chu hiche panmun loding chun alhengdoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin hiche mi sagi kilhengdoh ho chu solchah ho henga ahin puilut uvin ahileh solchah hon achung uva khut angamun ataopeh tauvin ahi.  
\v 7 Chuti chun Pathen thu chu amachal jingin atahsan mi hatah in akibe jingin, chule Juda te thempuho jong tamtah ajau uvin ahi.   
\s1 Stephen amat u  
\p
\v 8 Chuin Stephen chun, Pathen lungsetna le thaneina dimset in thil kidang le melchihna tampi mipi ho masanga abol in ahi.  
\v 9 Ahin nikhat chu chamlhat miho kikhop khomna a kon'in mi phabep, amaho chu Cyrene, Alexandria, Cilicia, le Asia gam'a konna Judah mi ahiuvin amaho chu ahungun Stephen chu ahung kinelpi tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Ahin Stephen in chihna le Lhagao dimset puma aseidoh thucheng anga chun koima adingjou pouvin ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin ama hon mipi themkhat atildoh un amaho kom'a chun Stephen in “Mose le Pathen ataitom,” thu kajauve atiuvin ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche asei uchun mipi chu alung handoh sah-uvin, chuin upaho leh houdan thuhil ho chun Stephen chu aman uvin vaipoloi anga ahin puilut un ahi.  
\v 13 Chuin jouthu hettohsahna asemun, “Hiche mipa hin Hou-In theng douna le Mose dan dounan thu aseiyin,  
\v 14 Chule Nazareth Jesu chun Hou-In hi ahin suhchim ding chule Mose'n eipeh u dan jong akhel ding ahi” tia asei kajauve, atiuvin ahi.  
\v 15 Hiche pettah chun vaipo loiho jouse chun Stephen chu ave sohkeiyun ahi, ajeh chu Stephen maiso chu vantil ho mai banga vahset ahi.   
\c 7  
\s1 Stephen in kihkonna a thu asei  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Thempu Chungnung chun Stephen chu adongin, “Hiche hehna thu ho hi dih em?” ati.  
\v 2 Chuin Stephen in adonbut in, “Sopite le Pate ho ngaiyuvin, Ipuluiyu Abraham Haran a achen masang, Mesopotamia gam'a aum laiyin Loupi Pathen chu ahenga ana kilah in,\x + \xo 7:2 \xt Semtilbu 12:1\x*  
\v 3 Hitin ana seiyin ahi, ‘na penna gam leiset le na insungmi hin dalhan lang, keiman kavetsah ding gam leiset a hungin’” ati.  
\v 4 Chuin Abraham'in Chaldea gam ahin dalhan apa thikah in Haran a ana chengin, chujouvin tua na chennau gamsunga hin ahin puilut in ahi.\x + \xo 7:4 \xt Semtilbu 11:31; \xt Semtilbu 12:4\x*  
\v 5 Ahinlah Pathen'in akengto ngapna ding kham gambeh neocha jong ana pepoi. Ahin Abraham'in chapa anei loulai vang'in nikhat le ama le ason achilhah ten hiche gam hi alo dingu ahi tin Pathen'in ana thutep in ahi.\x + \xo 7:5 \xt Semtilbu 12:7; 13:15; 15:18; 17:8\x*  
\v 6 Chuleh Pathen'in aseikit in nason na chilhate jong migama kum jali sohchang le bolgima um dingu ahi\x + \xo 7:6 \xt Semtilbu 15:13,14\x*  
\v 7 Ahin soh a kai nam mite chunga keiman thu katan ding, achaina le hiche gam'a hi hung kile kit uva keima eihou kit dingu ahi ati.\x + \xo 7:7 \xt Potdohbu 3:12\x*  
\v 8 Chule Pathen'in jong Abraham chu cheptan a kitepna thu anapen, chuin Abraham'in achapa Isaac ahin phat in aniget nin chep anatan in, chule hiche kitepna chu Isaac in jong Jacob ahina, chuleh Jacob in apului u som le ni alhin chan geiyin jong ahin boljom jingun ahi.\x + \xo 7:8 \xt Semtilbu 17:10-14; \xt Semtilbu 21:2-4; \xt Semtilbu 25:26; \xt Semtilbu 29:31—35:18\x*  
\v 9 Chuin hiche puluiho chu asopi pau Joseph chunga ana thangthip uvin, hijeh chun Egypt gam'a soh dingin ana johdoh uvin ahi. Ahin Pathen'in ana umpi jingin,\x + \xo 7:9 \xt Semtilbu 37:11; \xt Semtilbu 37:28; \xt Semtilbu 39:2,21\x*  
\v 10 Gentheina ho jouse a kon'in ana huhdoh in Egypt lengpa Pharaoh angsunga lungsetna anapen ahi. Chule Pathen'in Joseph chu kidangtah chihna anapen hijeh chun Pharaoh in Joseph chu Egypt gam pumpia vaipon ana pansah in chuleh aleng inpia jong mopon ana pansah in ahi.\x + \xo 7:10 \xt Semtilbu 41:39-41\x*  
\v 11 Ahin Egypt gam le Canaan gamsunga kel ahunglha tan ahileh gentheina sangtah ahunglhung tan hijeh chun ipuilui teu jong neh ding nei louvin anaum un ahi.\x + \xo 7:11 \xt Semtilbu 42:1,2\x*  
\v 12 Chuin Jacob in Egypt gamsunga neh aum nalaiye ti ahet phat in achate ipuilui teu chu neh cho dingin asolin ahi.  
\v 13 Anivei channa a anache uchun Joseph chu asopite henga ana kiphongin chuin asopite chu Pharaoh henga ana puilut in ahi.\x + \xo 7:13 \xt Semtilbu 45:1; \xt Semtilbu 45:16\x*  
\v 14 Chuin Joseph in mi asolin apa Jacob le a insung mite somsagi le nga ho chu ahenga dingin aga kousah tan ahi.\x + \xo 7:14 \xt Semtilbu 45:9,10,17,18; \xt Semtilbu 46:27\x*  
\v 15 Chuin Jacob chu Egypt gam'a anache in athitan ahi chule ipului teu jong anathi tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 7:15 \xt Semtilbu 46:1-7; \xt Semtilbu 49:33\x*  
\v 16 Chun alongdamsau chu Shechem a ahin pouvin Abraham'in Hamor chapa te kom'a ana chohna lhanmun'a chun avui tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 7:16 \xt Semtilbu 23:3-16; 33:19; 50:7-13; Joshua 24:32\x*  
\v 17 Pathen'in Abraham kom'a athutep guilhunna ding phat anaitah jeh chun miho chu Egypt gam'a chun hatah in apungun.\x + \xo 7:17 \xt Potdohbu 1:7,8\x*  
\v 18 Ahin Joseph hephalou lengthah khat Egypt lengvaipoa ahung pan phat in,  
\v 19 Hiche lengpa chun imiteu chu duha in abolin asugentheiyin chule achasen ho'u chu athina dingin anu le apa teu chu hunam'in ana paidoh sah in ahi.\x + \xo 7:19 \xt Potdohbu 1:10,11; \xt Potdohbu 1:22\x*  
\v 20 Hiche phat laitah chun Pathen mitvet a chapang hoitah Mose chu ana pengin, anu le apan inmun'ah lhathum hoitah in anasin lhonin ahi.\x + \xo 7:20 \xt Potdohbu 2:2\x*  
\v 21 Chuin anu le apan Mose chu apaidoh lhon tan ahileh Pharaoh chanun ana kimudoh in ama cha bang bangin ahin vahkhang tan ahi.\x + \xo 7:21 \xt Potdohbu 2:3-10\x*  
\v 22 Chuin Mose chu Egypt gamsung chihna ho jouse ahilun ahile ama chu thusei le natoh a thahat tah a hung hitan ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin Mose chu kum somli ahung hi phat hin nikhat chu asopite Israel te chu aga vetan ahile,\x + \xo 7:23 \xt Potdohbu 2:11-15\x*  
\v 24 Egypt mipa khat in Israel mikhat alamlou tah a abol chu amun chuin Mose chu ahungin Israel mipa chu ahuh in Egypt mipa chu athat tan ahi.  
\v 25 Mose chun hiche Israel mite chun Pathen'in keiho huhdoh dinga eihin solpeh ahi ti geldoh nauvinte tia anagel vang chun Israel mite chun ana geldoh pouvin ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin ajing nikhon amite agavet a ahileh, Israel mini ana kina lhonin hijeh chun aman jong chamna nasem kigon hiche miteni kom'a chun “Nangni sopi khat nahi lhon lou ham? Ipi dinga nakinah lhon ham?” atin ahile,  
\v 27 mikhat pa chun Mose chu ahin sondoh in, kon keiho chunga vaihom le thutana napan sah ham? tin ahin dongin,  
\v 28 “Janhia Egypt mipa khat natha banga chu keima jong neitha got ham?” atin ahi.  
\v 29 Chuin Mose’n hichu ajah phat chun, Egypt gam'a kon'in ajamin Midian gam apemin hiche mun'a chun chapa ni ahingin ahi.\x + \xo 7:29 \xt Potdohbu 18:3,4\x*  
\v 30 Chuin kum somli jouvin Vantil hamboh meikongin Mose chu Sinai mol toh kinai gamthip a chun ana kimupi in,\x + \xo 7:30 \xt Potdohbu 3:1-10\x*  
\v 31 Chuin Mose’n hichu amun athilmu chu kidang asah in, achenaiya agavet kigot le Pakai awgin chun ahin kouvin,  
\v 32 “Keima napului teu Pathen kahi, Abraham, Isaac, Jacob Pathen kahi,” ahin tin ahile Mose jong akicha behseh jengin ave ngam tapon ahi.  
\v 33 Chuin Pathen'in aseiyin, “Na kengchot sutlhan ajeh chu na dinna mun chu muntheng ahi.  
\v 34 Egypt gam'a kamite gentheina kamu tan, akanau aw kajan ahuhdoh dinga hung kumlha kahitai, hijeh chun tun keiman nangma hi Egypt gam'a ka nungsol kit nahi,” ati.  
\v 35 Chuin “Kon keiho chunga vaihom le thutana napan sah ham?” tia asanlou pau chu, Pathen'in hamboh lah a konna akimusah vantil jal chun vaipo ding le thutan dingin Pathen'in Mose chu alesol kit in ahile.\x + \xo 7:35 \xt Potdohbu 2:14\x*  
\v 36 Mose'n thil kidang le melchihna tamtah pumin Israel te chu Egypt gam'a kon'in ahin puidoh in twipisan le gamthip chu kum somli sungin ahung galkaiyun ahi.\x + \xo 7:36 \xt Potdohbu 7:3; \xt Potdohbu 14:21; \xt Minbu 14:33\x*  
\v 37 “Chuin Mose ama tah in Israel te kom'a anaseiyin, Pathen'in keima tobang themgao khat nangho lah a konna asodoh sah ding ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 7:37 \xt Danbu Ni Na 18:15,18\x*  
\v 38 Mose chu gamthip a ipului teu toh Pathen mite kikhop khomna a anaum khomin, Sinai Molchunga valtil in thu aseipeh chun, khonunga eiho jouse pehson dingin hinna thu eina lahpeh uvin ahi.\x + \xo 7:38 \xt Potdohbu 19:1—20:17; Danbu Ni Na 5:1-33\x*  
\v 39 Ahinlah Ipului teu chun Mose thusei ana ngai pouvin Egypt gam'a kinung le ding ana deijo un ahi.  
\v 40 Ipuilui teu chun Aaron kom'a aseiyun, “Eilamkai thei dingu pathen lim themkhat nei sempeh un ajeh chu Egypt gam'a konna eihin puidoh pau Mose hi iti hitam kahe tapouve,” atiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 7:40 \xt Potdohbu 32:1\x*  
\v 41 Chuin bongnou toh kilou milim khat asem uvin, hiche milim henga chun kilhaina gantha asem uvin, athilsem uchu akipapi uvin ahi.\x + \xo 7:41 \xt Potdohbu 32:2-6\x*  
\v 42 Chuin amahoa kon'in Pathen akihei mangin, Van'a ahsiho chu a pathen'u hi dingin adalha tan ahi! Chuin themgao lekhabun asei “Vo Israel kum somli gamthip a natham laiyuva nahin choiyu kilhaina gantha le thilto ho chu keima henga ding ham?\x + \xo 7:42 \xt Amos 5:25-27\x*  
\v 43 Ahipoi, nang hon Molech ponbuh le pathen Rephan ahsi hou dinga alim na semthu u chu napo le ji bouvui, hijeh a chu nangho Babylon gamsung chan a soh a kasol ding nahiuve,” ati.  
\v 44 Ipului teu chun gamthip noija chun Houbuh chu ana pole un Pathen'in Mose henga ana musah lim bang bang chun ana tungdoh ji un ahi.\x + \xo 7:44 \xt Potdohbu 25:9,40\x*  
\v 45 Kum phabep jouvin Joshua lamkaina a ipului teuvin hiche gam'a konna Pathen'in ana nodoh ho khopi mun analo uchun Pathen Houbuh chu ana polut un Leng David khang chanin ana um'in ahi.\x + \xo 7:45 \xt Joshua 3:14-17\x*  
\v 46 David chu Pathen mitmun deium ana chang'in, a-itih a Jacob Pathen chenna ding Hou-In sahna dingin ana thumin ahi.\x + \xo 7:46 \xt 2 Samuel 7:1-16; 1 Thusimbu 17:1-14\x*  
\v 47 Ahin hiche Hou-In chu Solomon in ana tungdoh in ahi.\x + \xo 7:47 \xt 1 Lgt 6:1-38; 2 Thusimbu 3:1-17\x*  
\v 48 Hijeng jong le hiche khut a kisa Hou-In a chun Chungnungpen Pathen chu achengpoi tin, Themgaovin aseiye.  
\v 49 “Van ka laltouna ahin leiset kakengto ngapna ahi, chutobang chenna ding inpha chu nei sahpeh thei ding ham?” tin Pakai chun adongin ahi.\x + \xo 7:49 \xt Isa 66:1,2\x*  
\v 50 Van le leiset ania kakhut a kasem hilou ham? tia asei banga chu.  
\v 51 “Nangho mi louchalte, thutah a dinga alungthim le ana ngong te ho, a imatih chana Lhagao Theng na doudalu hilou ham? Hichu na pului teuvin ana bola nang hon jong nabolu ahi.\x + \xo 7:51 \xt Isa 63:10\x*  
\v 52 Napului teuvin ana bolgim lou themgao khat umem? Chondih tah Messiah hung ding thu ana sei masaho chu ana that un ama tah jong na matsah un na that un ahi.  
\v 53 Chule Vantil a konna nalah son u Pathen danthu jeng jong henasa san nanit pouvin ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Stephen songa aselih u  
\p
\v 54 Stephen in athemmo nau thu asei chun Juda te lamkai ho chu alunghan sah lheh jengun chuin ama chu akhuttum ajel khumun ahi.  
\v 55 Ahin Lhagao Theng dimset in Stephen chun vanlam aven ahileh Pathen loupina le Jesu Pathen khut jetlam jabolna mun'a adin chu amun ahi.  
\v 56 Chuin aman amaho jah a, “Ven vankot akihona chule Pathen khut jetlam jabolna mun'a mihem chapa adin kamui,” ati.  
\v 57 Chuin ama hon akhut un anakol akisip un apengjah un ama chu anokhum jengun,  
\v 58 Khopi pamlanga akaidoh un songin asep un, chuin ama themmo chansah ho chun avon chu asut un Saul kiti khangdongpa kengbul'a chun akoiyun ahi.  
\v 59 Chuin songa ase pettah un Stephen chu ataovin, “Pakai Ka lhagao lan,” ati.  
\v 60 Chuin abohkhup in apengjah jengin, “Pakai abol ho jouseu hi amaho chonset in simpeh hih-in,” atin hiti chu athitan ahi.   
\c 8  
\s1 Saul in tahsan chate asuh genthei  
\p
\v 1 Saul jong chu Stephen kitha amittah a muho lah a khat ahin, ama tah in jong aphatsah ahi. Chuin hiche nikhoa kipat chun Jerusalem'a Houbung suhmangna dingin suhgentheina lentah ana kipan tan ahile Solchah ho tailou tahsan chate jouse chu Judea le Samaria gam'a ana kithe cheh tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin Pathen a dinga kipumpeh mi themkhat in Stephen chu lunghem tah in ana vuiyun ahi.  
\v 3 Ahin Saul chu achelen Houbungho chu ana sugentheiyin, a intin a alut in numei pasal akaidoh in songkul'a ana seplut jin ahi.\x + \xo 8:3 \xt Act 22:4,5; 26:9-11\x*   
\s1 Samaria mi phabep in tahsanna nei  
\p
\v 4 Ahinlah akithecheh tahsan chate chun achena lam lam uvah Jesu thudol Kipana Thupha chu alhangsam le tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Vetsahnan, Philip chu Samaria khopi sunga analut in miho kom'a Messiah chu ana samphong in ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin mipi chun Philip thusei chu lunglut tah in ana ngai uvin ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin lhagao boh tampi anodoh in ahileh amaho chu apeng uvin apotdoh tauvin chule lhangthi le elbai tampi jong aboldam in ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin hiche khopi achun kipana lentah alhung tan ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin Simon kiti doithem mikhat hiche gam'a chu kumsotpi anaum a ahin, ama chun milen khat kahi tia Samaria mite chu kidang satah a ana umsah ahi.  
\v 10 Mijouse aneova pat alen chan geiyin hiche pa chu “Milen khat-Pathen thahat” tia aseiyu ahi.  
\v 11 Chule ama chun adoiya konna phat sottah kidang satah a anaum sah jeh u chun ama hon asei jouse chu abonchan angai jiuvin ahi.  
\v 12 Ahivangin mipi ho chun Philip in Pathen Lenggam thu le Jesu Christa min'a thupha asei chu atahsan tauvin, hijeh chun numei pasal tampi twiyin baptize achang tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Hichun Simon jengin jong atahsan in twiyin baptize achang tan, chule Philip chena channa anung ajuitan, Philip in melchihna le thil kidang lentah tampi abol chu kidang asalheh jengin ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin Jerusalem'a um solchah hon Samaria miten Pathen thu asang tauve ti ajah phat un Peter le John chu asol tauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin alhun lhun lhonin hiche tahsan thahho chu Lhagao Theng achanna dingun atao tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chule tahsan thahho chunga chu Lhagao Theng hung loulai ahi, ajeh chu amaho chu Jesu min'a bou baptize chang nalaiyu ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin Peter le John in hiche tahsan thahho chunga chu khut angap lhona ahileh amaho chu Lhagao Theng achang tauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin Simon in Solchah ho khutngap jeh a miho Lhagao Theng achan u chu amun ahileh aman jong sum peh a hiche thahat chu kichoh ding agon,  
\v 19 “Kenjong hiche thaneina hi neijing kate chutile kenjong miho chunga khut kangap teng amaho jong Lhagao Theng chang dingu ahi!” ati.  
\v 20 Chuin Peter in adonbut in, “Nasum le nangma suhmangin umtha tan ajeh chun Pathen thilpeh hi chohtho dingin na ngaitoi,  
\v 21 Hichea hin nangman chan na neipoi, ajeh chu Pathen mitmun na lungthim adihpoi.  
\v 22 Hijeh chun na chonset lung heiyin lang, Pakai henga tao lechun aman na chonset lungput angaidam maithei ahi.  
\v 23 Ajeh chu nangma hi thangthipna a dimset leh chonset a kihen-oh nahi kamu chen tai,” ati  
\v 24 Chuin Simon chun Peter kom'a, “Hitobang kichat umtah naseiho hi kachunga alhun louna dingin Pakai kom'a nei taopeh in,” ati.   
\s1 Ethiopia kon nukisopa  
\p
\v 25 Chuin Samaria a photchetna le Pathen thu lhangsapna aneijou lhon chun, Peter le John chu Jerusalem jonin ahung kile lhonin Samaria kho mun tampi ah ahung kibangpa lhonin Kipana Thupha ahin lhangsam peh lhonin ahi.  
\v 26 Philip vang chu Pakai vantil, “Lhanglam a Jerusalem a pat Gaza jotna gamthip a chesuh lampi a khun chetan,” atipeh in ahi.  
\v 27 Chuin akipatdoh in achesuh tan ahileh Ethiopia gouching mikhat akimupin, ama chu Ethiopia lengnu noiya natong lentah nukiso ahin, hiche nukiso chu Jerusalem'a Pathen houva che ahi.  
\v 28 Chule ahung kile lama kangtalaiya hung touva Isaiah themgao lekhabu hi gingtah a ahin sim ahi.  
\v 29 Chuin Lhagao Theng in Philip henga chun ahin seiyin, “Chenlang kangtalaiya khun kilhon khom lhonin,” ati.  
\v 30 Chuin Philip chun aheng anaiyin ahileh mipan Isaiah themgao lekhabu asim chu ajan, hichun Philip in adongin “Nasim chu ipi kiseina ahi nahet nah em?” atile,  
\v 31 Mipa chun adonbut in, “Eihil ding mikhat aumlou le iti kahet ding ham?” atin ahi. Chuin mipa chun Philip chu akouvin hungin lang kangtalaiya toukhom hite ati.  
\v 32 Chule Pathen Lekhabu sunga asimmun chu hiche hi ahi, “Ama chu tha dinga kikai kelngoi nou bangin akaiyun, kelngoinou amul vouho ang sunga thipbeh chaa aum bangin, ama jong akam keh pon ahi.\x + \xo 8:32 \xt Isa 53:7,8\x*  
\v 33 Akineosahna lamin achunga adih a thutanna aum tapon, koipen'in akhang thusim asei ding hitam? Ijeh inem itile a hinkho chu leiset a konna alahdoh u ahitai.”  
\v 34 Chuin nukiso chun Philip chu adongin, “Themgaopa hin ama chung chang thudol asei ham ahilou le midang khat thudol asei ham nei seipeh in,” atin ahi.  
\v 35 Chuin in Philip jong chuche Pathen Lekhabu mun a konna pansa in Jesu thudol Kipana Thupha chu aseipeh pantan ahi.  
\v 36 Chuin ache che lhonin ahile twi umna khat ahin phah lhon phat in nukiso chun, “Ven! Hikom'a khun twi aum'e! Baptize kachan mona ding ipi um'em?” ati.  
\v 37 Hijeh chun Philip in, “Nalung naheiya nalungthim pumpia na tahsan pouleh hithei ding nahi,” ati. Chuin aman adonbut in, “Jesu Christa, Pathen Chapa ahi ti katahsan e,” atitai.  
\v 38 Chuin akangtalai lhon chu akham lhonin, twi lah a chun akumsuh lhonin Philip in ama chu baptize achansah tan ahi.  
\v 39 Chuin twi lah a konna ahung potdoh lhon chun Pakai Lhagaovin Philip chu alamang tan ahile, nukiso chun Philip chu amupha tapon, ahin alampi a chun kipah thanom tah in achetan ahi.  
\v 40 Chomkhat jouvin Philip chu sahlam a um Azotus mun'a chun akimudoh kit in, hichun aman Caesarea ahin phah chanin Kipana Thupha chu ahin sam phonglen ahi.   
\c 9  
\s1 Jesu Christa dinga Saul hinkho kikhel  
\p
\v 1 Ahin Saul vang chu Pakai nungjuiho gihsal le that dingin ahai hai nalaiyin, hijeh chun Thempu Chungnung henga achen,  
\v 2 Damascus khopia kikhopna in hoa dingin lekha agathumin, chule koi hijongleh hiche lampi tahsanho jouse chu numei hihen, pasal hijongleh akana Jerusalem ahin lhutna dingin kithopina agathumin ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche tupna nei puma ache laiyin Damascus khopi anaitah chun van'a kon'in phulou helouvin vah in akimvel ahin salin,  
\v 4 Chuin ama tol'a alhun chule “Saul! Saul! Ipi dinga nei bolset ham?” tia kisam aw khat ajan,  
\v 5 Chuin Saul in jong “Pakai nang koi nahim?” tin adong tan ahi. Chuin aw chun ahin donbut in “Keima Jesu, nabolset jingpa chu kahi!  
\v 6 Tun kipatdoh in khopi sunga khun lut in nabol ding ho naki seipeh ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 7 Chuin Saul toh kilhon khom ho chu paopoh loubeh in aum tauvin ahi, ajeh chu Saul kom'a thusei aw chu ajauvin ahin koima la amu pouvin ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin Saul chu tol'a konna ahung dindoh a amit ahasah le kho amu tapon hijeh chun alhon khompi hon akhut in akaiyun Damascus khopi sung alut tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin khopi sunga chun nithum sungin an nelou twidon louvin aumden tan ahi.   
\s1 Ananias in Saul baptize achansah  
\p
\v 10 Chuin Damascus khopi sunga tahsan mikhat amin Ananias kitipa chu Pakaiyin akimusah in “Ananias!” tin akouvin ahileh amapan, “Hikom'a kaumnai Pakai!” atin ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin Pakaiyin adonbut in “Na masanga lampi jangkeiya khun chenlang Judas in'a khun galut tan, chule insunga khu nalut tengleh Tarsus gammi Saul kitipa chu gahol tan ajeh chu ama kahenga atao pettah ahi.  
\v 12 Chule hiche pa khun Ananias kiti mikhat ahenga hunga aluchunga khut angap a chutengleh kho amukit ding khu kamusah ahi,” ati.  
\v 13 Ahivangin Ananias in adonbut in “Pakai hiche mipa hin Jerusalem'a tahsan chate kichat umtah a abol genthei thu mi tamtah a konna kajah ahitai,  
\v 14 chule hoilai mun hijongleh nangma min kouho jouse amat a songkul'a akhum theina dinga thempu pipui hon thaneina apeh u ahitai,” ati.  
\v 15 Ahin Pakaiyin aseiyin, “Chen, ajeh chu Saul khu chidang namdang te le lengho chuleh Israel te henga kathu lhangsam dinga ka lhendoh ahitai,  
\v 16 Chule tua hi kamin jal'a itobang genthei athoh ding ham kavetsah ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 17 Chuin Ananias chu achen ahileh Saul chu amutan hichun aluchunga akhut angamin aseitai, “Sopi Saul, kho namu kitna ding le Lhagao Thenga na dimsetna dinga lampia nakimu sah Pakai Jesu chun nahenga eihin sol ahi,” ati.  
\v 18 Chuin apettah chun lip tobang thil khat Saul mit a kon chun ahung kilehlhan ahileh Saul chun kho amutan ahi. Chutah chun Saul chu akipatdoh in baptize achang tan ahi.  
\v 19 Chujouvin Saul chun an themkhat anen ahileh athahat doh kittan, chuin Damascus khopi sunga tahsan chate kom'a chun nikho phabep aum den tan ahi.  
\v 20 Chule apettah chun Jesu thudol chu asamphong pantan kikhopna in tin'ah, “Jesu chu Pathen Chapa ahi,” tin asam le tan ahi.  
\v 21 Chuin athu lhangsap japha jousen kidang asauvin, “Hiche pa hi Jerusalem'a Jesu seijui ho suhmang ding gopa chu hilou ham?” atiuvin ahi. Chule “Hikom'a hi seijui ho man ding le kanchoma thempu ho henga kai dinga hung hilou ham?” atiuvin ahi  
\v 22 Saul thulhangsap chu ahung thahat cheh cheh jeng tan ahileh Damascus khopia um Juda mite chun Jesu chu Messiah ahi ti avetsahna apeh ho chu aneljou tapouvin ahi.   
\s1 Judah hon Saul tha dia anga u  
\p
\v 23 Chuche phat chomkhat jou chun Judah mite phabep khat ahung khomun ama chu tha ding agouvin,\x + \xo 9:23 \xt 2 Crth 11:32,33\x*  
\v 24 Ama chu thateina dingin khopi kelkot dunga sun le jan in achanglhi jingun, ahin mihon tha ding agonu thu chu aseipeh un,  
\v 25 Hijeh chun seijui ho mi phabep khat chun jankah in Saul chu boma akhumun khopi bang onglai khat ah khaovin akhai lha tauvin ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin Saul chu Jerusalem ahung lhunin, seijui ho kimupi ding agon ahileh amaho abonun akichauvin ahi ajeh chu seijui dihtah ahi ding chu atahsan lou u ahi!  
\v 27 Chuin Barnabas chun Saul chu solchah ho henga apuilut in Damascus lampia Saul in Pakai akimupi thu le Pakaiyin Saul henga asei thu ho abonchan solchah ho henga aseipeh in chule Damascus khopia Saul in Jesu min'a hangsan tah a thu asei jong chu aseipeh in ahi.  
\v 28 Chuin Saul chu solchah ho chutoh aum khom tan, Jerusalem kimvela avahle un hangsan tah in Pakai minin thu alhangsam tan ahi.  
\v 29 Chuin Greek pao tho Juda te toh akinil un ahile Juda miho chun tha ding agouvin ahi.  
\v 30 Seijui hon chuche thu ajah phat un Caesarea lama apuisuh un achenna Tarsus lama asol mang tauvin ahi.  
\v 31 Chuin Judea gam le Galilee gamsung chule Samaria gamsung pumpia Houbung chu mongtah in aum tauvin chule seijui hon Pakai agin jeh u chun athahat cheh cheh uvin ahi. Chule Lhagao Theng in aumpi jeh u chun seijui jong akibe jingin ahi.   
\s1 Peter in Aeneas asuhdam  
\p
\v 32 Chujongleh Peter chu munkhat a kon'in munkhat ah avahle len chuin Lydda khopia seijui ho vil dingin ahung kumsuh in ahile,  
\v 33 Hikom'a chun Aeneas kiti mikhat langthia kumget jen jalkhun a lumpa chu aga mudoh tan,  
\v 34 Chuin Peter in ajah a “Aeneas, Jesu Christan na damsah ahitai! Thouvin lang nalupna kijeldoh tan,” ati. Chupet tah chun ama adamtan ahi.  
\v 35 Chuin Lydda le Sharon khopi sunga mijouse chun Aeneas in lam ajot a avale chu amu uvin, abonchauvin Pakai lamah ahung kihei tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Peter in Tabitha acho hing  
\p
\v 36 Chuin Joppa atiu mun a chun seijui mikhat Tabitha (Greek paova Dorcas) atiu chu aumin, amanu chun midang dingin thilpha abol jingin, genthei ho akithopi jingin ahi.  
\v 37 Amanu chu ahung dammo in athitan ahileh atahsa chu asiltheng uvin vui dingin indan chungnunga chun alupsah tauvin ahi.  
\v 38 Ahivangin seijui ho chun Peter chu Lydda kom'a aum'e tithu ajauvin hijeh chun mini asol uvin, Peter henga “Lungset tah in aganna thei penin hungin,” tin aga kousah tauvin ahi.  
\v 39 Chuin Peter chu akouva che teni chutoh ahung kile khomin ahileh ahung lhun lhun chun ama hon Peter chu indan chungnunga chun apuitouvun ahileh insunga chun meithai ho adimset uvin kap pumin a sangkhol hou le von dang Dorcas in adam laiya ana bolpeh hou chu avetsah un ahi.  
\v 40 Ahivangin Peter chun abonchauvin insunga kon chun asoldoh in chuin ama adilsun atahsa alupsah u chu aven “Thoudoh in Tabitha,” tin atao tan ahileh amit ahung hahdoh in, chuin amanun Peter amu phat in ahung toudoh tan ahi.  
\v 41 Chuin aman akhut in akai dingin chule meithai ho le seijui ho chu abonchan akoulut in amanu chu ahingin apetan ahi.  
\v 42 Hiche thu chu khopi sunga akithang soh tan ahileh mi tamtah in Pakai atahsan tan ahi.  
\v 43 Chule Peter chu Joppa mun'a savun sem Simon in'ah nisottah aumden tan ahi.   
\c 10  
\s1 Peter le Cornelius  
\p
\v 1 Rome te sepai lamkai Cornelius atiu mikhat Caesarea ah ana chengin, ama chu Italia loi atiu sepai jalamkai ahi.  
\v 2 Amapa chu Pathen ngaisah tah le a insung mijouse toh Pathen gingmi ahin; migenthei ho hongphal tah a pejing le Pathen henga tao jing mi ahi.  
\v 3 Nikhat nilhah lam nidan thum donin mu aneiyin athilmu achun Pathen vantil khat ahenga ahungin “Cornelius!” ahung tin ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Cornelius chun kicha tah in aven, “Ipi ham Pakai,” tin adong tan ahi. Chule Vantil chun ahin donbut in, “Nataona le migenthei ho dinga nathilpeh ho chu Pathen'in thilto bangin nasanpeh tai!  
\v 5 Tun nangman mi themkhat solin lang Joppa a um Simon Peter kitipa khu gakousah tan.  
\v 6 Ama twikhanglen panga Simon kiti savun sem mikhat in'ah aum'e,” ati.  
\v 7 Chuin vantil in adalhah lhah in Cornelius chun a insunga lhacha ni le akinbol a pang jing Pathen ngaisah tah sepai ho lah a khat akouve.  
\v 8 Thilsoh jouse aseipeh jouvin amaho chu Joppa ah asol tan ahi.  
\v 9 Ajing nikho in Cornelius thupo ho khopi sung alhun ding konun Peter chu indan chunga tao dingin ahung kaldoh in hichu sunkim don ahi.  
\v 10 Chule ama chu agilkel in, ahivangin aneh ding an asem laitah un ama agaochangin,  
\v 11 Chuin vankot akihona lekha pheng lentah tobang khat aning lia ahung kikhai lhah amun,  
\v 12 Chuin hiche lekha pheng lentah tobang sunga chun ganhing namkim le tol'a vah ganhing chule chunga leng vacha ho aumun,  
\v 13 Chuin aw khat in ahenga ahin seiyin, “Peter, kipatdoh inlang chule kithan lang nen,” ati.  
\v 14 Chuin Peter in adonbut in, “Ahipoi Pakai, ajeh chu imatih chanin keiman Juda te dan thu dungjuiya sathenglou le saboh ka nekhapoi,” ati.  
\v 15 Ahivangin aw chun ahinsei kit in, “Pathen'in asuhthengsa chu athenglou tidan,” ati.  
\v 16 chuti chun thumvei jen kibang chet in mu aneiyin chujouvin hetmanlou kah in lekha pheng lentah tobang chu van'a khai touvin aum tan ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin Peter chun gaova athilmu chu ipi kiseina ahidem tia lunggim tah a ana um laitah in Cornelius in ahin sol miho chun Simon in chu ahin holdoh un, amaho chu kelkot ah ana ding uvin,  
\v 18 Amaho chun hiche laiya hi Simon Peter kiti mikhat cheng em tin adongun ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin Peter in gaova athilmu chu ipi ahidem tia ana gel jing laiyin Lhagao Thengin ahenga thu ahin seiyin, “Mithum tah in nangma nahol'e,  
\v 20 Kipatdoh in, kumsuh inlang amaho toh kilhon ding khu thase hihbeh in, chule lungkham hih in ajeh chu keiman amaho khu kahin sol ahi,” ati.  
\v 21 Chuin Peter akum suh in amaho kom'a “Nahol u mipa chu keima kahi, ipi dinga hung nahiuvem?” tin adong tan ahile,  
\v 22 ama hon adonbut-un, “Keiho hi Cornelius kiti Pathen gingtah mi chule Juda ten ajabol u Rome sepai jalamkai pa chun eihin sol u ahin, chule nangma thusei hi a insung mite toh angai theina dinga vantil theng khat in thu apeh bang banga nakouva hung kahiuve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin Peter in amaho chu akoulut in a in'ah jankhat agesah in, ajingin Joppa a konna sopi themkhat toh akilhon tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Cornelius henga Peter thusei  
\p
\v 24 Ajing nikhon amaho Caesarea ahunglhung tauvin ahile Cornelius in a insung mite le aloi agol ho ana koukhomin ana ngah tauvin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin Peter insunga alut in ahile Cornelius chu akengbula abohkhup in chibai abohtan ahi.  
\v 26 Ahinlah Peter chun akai dingin, “Dingdoh in keijong nang banga mihem khat kahi bouve!” ati.  
\v 27 Chuti chun amani akihoulim lim lhonin insunga mitampi kikhop khomna achun alut lhonin,  
\v 28 Chuin Peter in amaho henga chun, “Judah mikhat hitia chidang namdang te in'a alut hi Judah te chonna dan toh kitoh lou ahi naheuve, Ahin Pathen'in koima aboh le athenglou tia kagel louna dinga eimusah ahitai.  
\v 29 Hijeh a chu lungthoi louhel a eihin kou banga kahung jeng ahi. Tun ipi dinga neihin kou ham seitan,” ati.  
\v 30 Chuin Cornelius in adonbut in, “Nili masang, tuphat chet nilhah lang nidan thum donin ka insunga kataovin ahileh, hetmanlou kah in ka masang laitah a ponbanga kivon mikhat ka anga ahung dingin;  
\v 31 Hitin ahin seiyin ahi, ‘Cornelius Pathen'in nataona ajatan genthei ho dinga na thilpha bol jong amutai!  
\v 32 Tun nangman Joppa a mi solin lang, Simon Peter kiti mipa khu gakousah tan. Ama twikhanglen panga Simon kiti savun sempa in'ah aum'e’ ati.  
\v 33 Hijeh a chu nangma kouva mi kahin sol ahin, nahung hi apha lheh jenge, chule tun Pakaiyin thu napehho ngai dingin hikom'a Pathen angsunga hin ibon chauvin iki khom tauve,” ati.  
\v 34 Chuin Peter in adonbut in, “Pathen'in mi lungset tum aneipoi ti kichen tah in kamutai;\x + \xo 10:34 \xt Danbu Ni Na 10:17\x*  
\v 35 Ahin chitin namtin lah a koi hijongleh Ama ginga thildih bol ho chu ama dinga lahthei ahi.  
\v 36 Chule hiche hi Israel chatea dinga Kipana Thupha ahi–Jesu Christa mijouse Pakai vanga Pathen toh kichamna aum hi.  
\v 37 John in twilut thudol ahin lhangsap pat a pat Galilee a kipan Judea gam pumpia ipi thilsoh em nang hon naheuve.  
\v 38 Chule Pathen'in Nazareth Jesu chu Lhagao Theng le thahatna a thao anua chule Jesu avalea thilpha abol ho leh Pathen'in aumpi jal'a satan suhgima umho aboldam chu nang hon naheuve.  
\v 39 Chule keiho solchah ho hi Judah gam pumpi le Jerusalem'a athilbol ho jouse hettohsah kahiuve. Ama chu thingpel chunga akhaisang un athat tauve.  
\v 40 Ahin Pathen'in ama chu anithum nin akaithouvin aki phondohsah tan ahi.  
\v 41 Hichu mijouse henga hilouvin, athu hettohsah dinga Pathen'in ana lhendohsa, athodoh jouva ama toh nekhom le donkhom keiho henga kiphong ahi.  
\v 42 Chule Jesu chu mihing le mithi ho jouse thutan ahi ti thudol hi hille ding le hettohsah dinga keiho hi thu eipeh u ahi.  
\v 43 Ama tahsan ho jouse Amin jal a achonset nau kingaidam ding ahi tia themgao ho jousen a hettohsah u chu ama chu ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Chidang namdang ho Lhagao Theng achan u  
\p
\v 44 Chuin Peter in thu hicheng asei jing laiyin athu ngaiho jouse chunga Lhagao Theng ahung chutan ahile,  
\v 45 Peter toh hung khom Judah mi atahsan ho chun chidang namdang te chunga jong Lhagao Theng akipeh chu kidang asalheh jengun ahi.  
\v 46 Ijeh-inem itile ama hon paochom paochoma thu aseiyuva Pathen avahchoi uchu ajah u ahi.  
\v 47 Chuin Peter in adong un, “Eiho banga Lhagao Theng changa hite ho baptize chan louna dinga twi kham theiya koi umam?” ati.  
\v 48 Chuin aman Jesu Christa min'a baptize chang dingin amaho chu thu apetan, chujouvin Cornelius in amaho henga nikho phabep um dingin alhotan ahi.   
\c 11  
\s1 Chidang namdang ten Jesu Christa tahsan  
\p
\v 1 Chidang namdang ten Pathen thu akisan thu chu Judah gam'a um solchah ho le seijui dang ho henga gangtah in alhung tan;  
\v 2 Ahinlah Peter Jerusalem ahung le-lhun phat in Judahmi atahsanho chun ana oimo un;  
\v 3 “Chidang namdang te insunga nalut in chule an jong naga nehkhompi e,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Peter in amaho heng ah thilsoh jouse kicheh tah in aseipeh in hitin aseiyin ahi.  
\v 5 “Keima Joppa khopia kauma katao jing laiyin gao changin mu kaneiyin, lekha pheng lentah tobang aning lin van'a kon'in ahung kikhai lhan, keima komtah ahung geiyin;  
\v 6 Chuin keiman hiche lekha pheng lentah tobang sung chu kaven ahileh leiset chunga umsa akengli ho leh gamsa chule aop a kithol le chunga leng vacha kamun,  
\v 7 Chuin van'a konna awgin khat kajan ‘Peter, thoudoh inlang, kitha inlang nen’” ati.  
\v 8 Ahipoi Pakai, keiho Judah te chonna danin aboh le athenglou tia asei jouse imacha kane khapoi kati.  
\v 9 “Ahin van'a konna awgin chun avelin ahin seikit in, ‘Pathen'in asuhthengsa thil khat chu athenglou tihih in,’” ati.  
\v 10 Hiche thilsoh chu thumveijen kijomin eimusah in chujouvin abonchan van'a akikhai tou kit tan ahi.  
\v 11 Chutah chun Caesarea a konna mithum hung kisol ho chu kaum nau inmun ahunglhung paiyun ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin Lhagao Theng in kahenga ahin seiyin amaho chutoh kilhon'a chule amaho chidang namdang ahijeh a ima lungthoina neilou dingin ahin seiyin ahi. Chuin sopi migup chun ei kilhonpi uvin gangtah in ahin solpau in chu kaga lhung tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Chuin amapa chun thilsoh umchan jouse chu keiho henga chun aseiyin, ahenga vantil akilah a Joppa a mi solin lang Simon Peter kiti mipa khu gakousah tan,  
\v 14 Chutengleh aman nang le na insung mite jouse huhhingna thu naseipeh ding ahi! ati.  
\v 15 Chuin Peter chun aseikit in, “Thusei kahinpan in ahileh abul'a eiho chunga ahung kibuh lhah bangin amaho jouse chunga Lhagao Theng ahung kibunglhan,  
\v 16 Chun Pakaiyin ‘John in twiya baptize achansah ahin ahinlah nangman Lhagao Thenga baptize na chansah ding ahi’ tia Pakai thusei chu kalunga ahung kilang in ahi.\x + \xo 11:16 \xt Act 1:5\x*  
\v 17 Chule eihon Pakai Jesu Christa itahsan nikhouva Pathen'in eipeh u Lhagao Theng chu chidang namdang te jong apeh ahitah le kei chu koi kahi a Pathen masanga kadin ding ham?” atin ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin midang hon chuche thu chu ajah phat un athip tauvin Pathen avahchoi tauvin ahi. Chule ama hon aseiyun, “Pathen'in chidang namdang te dinga jong chonset lungheina ding le tonsot hinna akisan theina ding uva phatpha apeh hi imu tauve,” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Antioch mun a houbung  
\p
\v 19 Alangkhat ah Stephen thi jouva seijui ho kibol gentheina jeh a jamcheh ho chu Phoenicia, Cyprus le Syria gam'a Antioch chan geiyin ajamun, chule Judah te henga bou Pathen thu alhangsam un ahi.\x + \xo 11:19 \xt Act 8:1-4\x*  
\v 20 Hijeng jong le Cyprus le Cyrene gam'a konna Antioch khopia che seijui phabep ho chun chidang namdang te henga Pakai Jesu thu alhangsam uvin ahi.  
\v 21 Pakai thahatna amaho chunga aum jeh chun chidang namdang te lah a mi tamtah in Pakai lama lung aheiyun atahsan tauvin ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin Jerusalem'a Houbung in hiche thu ajah phat un Barnabas chu Antioch a asol tauvin ahile,  
\v 23 Amun alhun phat in Pathen phatthei bohna chu amun akipah lheh jengin hichun aman seijui ho chu Pakaiya dihtah a um jing dingin atilkhouvin ahi.  
\v 24 Ajeh chu Barnabas chu miphatah Lhagao Thenga dimjing le tahsanna a dettah mi ahin, mi tamtah Pakaiyah ahin puilutbe uvin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin Barnabas chu Tarsus lama Saul hol dingin ana chepai tan ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin amu phat in Antioch lama ahin nungpui kit in amani Antioch houbunga chun kumlhung keiyin aumden lhonin mipi tamtah ahil jing lhonin ahi. Hiche Antioch a hi seijui ho Christian tia akou masat penu ahi.  
\v 27 Hiche phatlai hin themgao phabep Jerusalem'a kon Antioch a acheuvin,  
\v 28 Amaho lah a Agabus atiu themgaopa chu kikhop khomna khat a ading doh in lhagaovin Rome gamsung pumpia kel nasatah hunglhung ding ahi tin aphondoh sah tan ahi (Hiche gao thu hi Claudius vaipoh laiyin aguilhung in ahi).\x + \xo 11:28 \xt Act 21:10\x*  
\v 29 Chuin Antioch a um seijui ho chun Judah gam'a um sopi hoa dinga kithopina thot dingin agellha tauvin ahile abonchauvin atamthei penin atohkhom tauvin ahi.  
\v 30 Chuin hiche athil tokhomu chu Barnabas le Saul in Jerusalem'a Houbung upaho khut a apehlut lhon dingin ngansena anei tauvin ahi.   
\c 12  
\s1 Jacob kitha chule Peter songkul a kikhum  
\p
\v 1 Chuin hiche phatlai chun Leng Herod Agrippa chun Houbung sunga seijui phabep ho chu ahin sugim pan tan ahi.  
\v 2 Chuti chun John sopipa solchah Jacob chu chemjamin ana that tan ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche thilsoh hin Judah te akipasah chu Herod in amu phat in Peter jong chu aman in, (Hiche thilsoh hi Kalchuh Kut kimanlai ahi).  
\v 4 Chuin ama chu Songkul'a akhum tan angah dingin Sepai lili a kiloikhom loili akoiyin ahi. Herod in Kalchuh Kut kichai tengleh mipi anga Peter chu dinsah dinga lung angaito ahi.\x + \xo 12:4 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-27\x*  
\v 5 Ahin Peter songkul'a aum phat chun Houbung mite chu lunglut tah in ama dingin atao tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin mipi anga dinsah dinga agot jan chun Peter chu sepai ni kikah a thihkhao ni a kihen a ihmu ahin; angah ho jong chu kotbula dingah ahiuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin hetmanlou kah in vah hattah khat in aumna mun chu ahin salvah in chule Pakai vantil chu Peter angsunga ahung dingin, chuin Vantil chun Peter pangpeh abengin “Thoudoh loiyin,” tin asukhang tan ahile akihenna thihkhao jong chu akilham tan ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin Vantil chun Peter jah a “Kivondoh loiyin lang na kengchot kisen,” asei bangin Peter in aboltan ahile Vantil chun “Napon kisil inlang kanung hin juijin,” tin thu apetan ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin Peter in aumna mun chu adalhan Vantil nung chu ajui tan ahi. Ahin Peter in thilsoh jouse chu gaochanga munei bangin akigelin atah tah ahilam ahedoh pon ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin amanin kot ngah masa le anina akhel phat lhonin khopi sung lam jotna a thih kot phung chu agei lhonin, kot chu amani dingin achamin akihong jengin, chuin amani achedoh lhonin khosung lamlen khat ajot lhung lhonin ahile, hichun Vantil chun ama adalha pai tan ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin Peter in kho ahin hedoh tan, “Thilsoh chu atah ahi! Pakaiyin a Vantil ahin solin Herod lengpa leh Judah lamkai hon kachunga abolgot u thilsea kon'in eihuhdoh e,” ati.  
\v 12 Chuin aman thilsoh ho ahin hetdoh phat in John Mark nu Mary in'a achetan ahile mi tamtah ana taokhomun,  
\v 13 Chuin aman kot chu akiuvin ahile soh numei Rhoda kiti nu chu kot hong dingin ahungin ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin numei nu chun Peter awso ahi ahetdoh phat chun kot jong hong louvin insunga anung lhailut in miho jah a chun “Peter kotbula adinge!” agatin ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin miho chun amanu jah a “Angol thim nahim,” atiuve, ahin amanu chun ahi mong monge ati phat chun amaho chun akhutile “Avantil hinah ta,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Alangkhat ah Peter in kot chu akiu kiu jengin ahi. Achainakeiya ama hon kot chu ahona avet ule Peter chu amu phat un kidang asa lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin Peter in amaho chu thipbeh a um dingin akhut in avetsah in, amaho kom'a chun Pakaiyin kidang tah a songkul'a konna ahin puidoh dan thusim chu aseipeh tan ahi. Chule “Hiche thu chu Jacob le asopiho seipeh un,” atin ama hikom'a kon chun munchoma achetan ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin kho ahung vah phat in sepai ho chun i-atileh Peter chu songkul'a konna potdoh thei ham tin alungdong lheh jeng uvin ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin Herod lengpan sepai ho kom'a chun Peter chu phatecha aholna dingun thu apen ahinlah amu dehlou phat un, songkul ngah a pang sepai ho chu thudoh aneiyin ajonan amaho chu athat tan ahi. Chujou chun Herod lengpa jong Judah gam dalhan phat chomkhat um dingin Caesarea ajon tan ahi.   
\s1 Herod thi  
\p
\v 20 Tun Herod lengpa chu Tyre le Sidon mite chunga alunghang lheh jeng tan ahileh ama hon thalheng in mi asol uvin amaho chun Herod lengpa noiya natong Blastus chu athujo jouvun Herod lengpa toh chamna sem dingin aga thum tauvin ahi. Ajeh chu Tyre le Sidon gamsunga ding neh le chah hi Herod lengpa gamsunga konna hungji ahi.  
\v 21 Chuin Herod in athum nau chu asanpeh in akitep nikhou ahung lhunin Herod in aleng von ahin kivonin, aleng touna a atouvin amaho kom'a chun thu asei tan ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin mipi ho chun “Hiche hi mihem awso ahipoi, Pathen aw ahi,” atiuvin hasap in asam tauvin ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin mipi hon chutia asap pettah u chun Herod in Pathen loupina peh sangin ama akiloupi sah tan ahile Pakai vantil in Herod chunga natna ahin lhunsah tan, chuti chun lungin anen athitan ahi.  
\v 24 Alangkhat ah Pathen thu chu akithe jal jingin seijui apung jingin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin Barnabas le Saul in Jerusalem'a akin lhon achai lhon phat in John Mark apui lhonin akile tauvin ahi.   
\c 13  
\s1 Paul le Barnabas, Cyprus achelhon  
\p
\v 1 Antioch Houbung sunga Themgao le mihil ho chu, Barnabas, Simeon (mivompa), Lucius (Cyrene mi), Manaen (Herod Antipas golpa), chule Saul ahiuve.  
\v 2 Chuin Nikhat amaho hin anngola Pathen ahoukhom pet un Lhagao Theng in amaho kom'a chun “Barnabas le Saul chu kakouna natong dingin lhandoh tauvin,” ahin tin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin ama hon anngola taona hatah a anei jouvun amani chunga chun khut angam un, ataopeh jouvun asoldoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Barnabas le Saul chu Lhagao Theng in asoldoh lhon tan ahile, amani Seleucia kongkai mun'a achesuh lhonin chuin Cyprus twikol jon dingin konga atou lhon tan ahi.  
\v 5 Chuche mun'a Salamis khopi alhun lhon phat in Judah te kikhop khomna hoa alut lhonin Pathen thu asamphong le lhon tan ahi. Chule John Mark jong amani kithopi dingin akilhon uvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin amani twikol sung pumpi a chun khopi khat a kon'in khopi khat ah avahle lhonin Paphos chan in ache lhonin ahile hiche lai mun'a chun Bar-Jesu kiti Judah mi doichoi le themgao lhem khat akimupi lhonin ahi.  
\v 7 Chule amapa chu gamvaipo miching tah Sergius Paulus kom'a uma ahi. Chuin gamvaipo pa chun Pathen thu angai nom jeh chun Barnabas le Saul chu akou tan ahi.  
\v 8 Ahinlah Elymas kiti doichoi mikhat ahung kikum lut in gamvaipo chun Barnabas le Saul thusei chu atahsan louna tei dingin hiche teni thusei hi ngaipeh hih in tin aseiyin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin Paul tia jong kihe Saul chu Lhagao Theng adimset in, chule aman doichoi mipa chu aven,  
\v 10 “Nangma Diabol chapa, Jou le jona milhemlha, thilpha jouse dinga melma pa! Pathen lamdih a konna mihem puimang ding hi nangah louhel ding ham?  
\v 11 Ven tun Pakai mijepna khut chu na chunga hung chu ding chule namit choding phat chomkhat khovah namu louding ahitai.”  
\v 12 Hiche thilsoh chu gamvaipo chun amu phat in ama jong seijui ho lah a ajao tan ahi ajeh chu Pakai thudol thuhil chu kidang asah val jeng ahi.  
\v 13 Chuin Paul le alhon khompi ho chun Paphos dalhan Pamphylia jon dingin konga akitolun Perga mun'a akinga tauvin, chule hiche mun'a kon chun John Mark chu Jerusalem lama akile tan ahi.   
\s1 Antioch le Pisidia khoa Paul le Barnabas  
\p
\v 14 Ahin Paul le Barnabas vang chu keng lam in Pisidia gam'a Antioch chan ache lhonin, chuin cholngah nikhon amani jong kikhom dingin kikhop khomna in ah alut lhon tan ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin angaiya Mose le Themgao lekhabu asim jouvun kikhopna a lamkai hon amani kom'a chun “Sopi teni mipi ho tilkhouna dinga seinom nanei lhon le hung sei lhonin,” tin phat apeuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Paul ading doh in akhut alhaang in mipi ho chu thipbeh cha a um dingin aseiyin, chuin aman aseitai, “Israel mite ho leh Pathen ging'ah chidang namdang te ho, ngaiyuvin,  
\v 17 Hiche Israel nampi Pathen chun ipu ipateu ana lhengdoh in Egypt gam'a chun apunsah uvin chule thahat tah nampi khat in ahin semdoh tan ahi. Chuin athahat nan Egypt mite khut ah asoh chan nauva kon'in ahin huhdoh in,”\x + \xo 13:17 \xt Potdohbu 1:7; \xt Potdohbu 12:51\x*  
\v 18 Gamthip noiya kum somli jen ahin puiyin,\x + \xo 13:18 \xt Minbu 14:34; Danbu Ni Na 1:31\x*  
\v 19 Chuin Canaan gamsunga nam sagi jen asumang in, agamsungu chu Israel ten alo dingin apetan ahi.\x + \xo 13:19 \xt Danbu Ni Na 7:1; \xt Joshua 14:1\x*  
\v 20 Hiche thilsoh hi kum 450 sunga soh ahi. Chujouvin Israel chate chunga vaihom dingin Pathen thutan vaihom ho ana pen amaho chun Samuel themgao pa khang chanin vai anahom un ahi.\x + \xo 13:20 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 2:16; \xt 1 Samuel 3:20\x*  
\v 21 Chuin mipi chun leng ana thum'un, ahile Pathen'in Benjamin phunga kon Kish chapa Saul chu ana pen ama chun kum somli lengvai anapon ahi.\x + \xo 13:21 \xt 1 Samuel 8:5; \xt 1 Samuel 10:21\x*  
\v 22 Ahin Pathen'in Saul chu leng mun'a kon'in ana ladoh in David chu ana tung tan ahi. Pathen'in David thudol'a hitin ana seiye “Keiman kalung gottah mi Jesse Chapa David kamutai, aman kalunggot jouse abol ding ahi” ati.\x + \xo 13:22 \xt 1 Samuel 13:14; \xt 1 Samuel 16:12; Labu 89:20\x*  
\v 23 Chule Pathen'in Israel te huhdoh dinga athutep Jesu chu leng David insunga kon ahi.  
\v 24 Ama ahung masang'in twilutsah John in Israel mipi jousen chonset lung aheiya Pathen kom'a akile kit uva chule twiya Baptize achanna dingu thu ana lhangsam in ahi.\x + \xo 13:24 \xt Mk 1:4; Lk 3:3\x*  
\v 25 Chuin John in atoh ding kin achai phat in aman adongin “Kei hi Messiah nei hisah uham? Kahipoi! Ahin Ama hungvah ding ahi, chule keima akengchot khao sutlha a pang asolchah khat dinga jong lhing jou kahipoi.”\x + \xo 13:25 \xt Jn 1:20; \xt Matt 3:11; Mk 1:7; Lk 3:16; Jn 1:27\x*  
\v 26 Sopite, Abraham son ho le chidang namdang Pathen ging mite ho, Hiche huhhingna thupha hi eiho dinga hung kisol ahi.  
\v 27 Jerusalem mite le alamkai teuvin themgao hon Jesu thudol aseiyu ahilam ahepouve. Chusang'in themmo achanun hiche jeng jong hin cholngah niseh a themgao ho thucheng aguilhun sah ahi.  
\v 28 Chule dan dungjuiya thana ding themmona jong amu pouvin, ahin Pilate henga chun atha teitei na dingin angeh un ahi.\x + \xo 13:28 \xt Matt 27:22,23; Mk 15:13,14; Lk 23:21-23; Jn 19:15\x*  
\v 29 Chuin themgaovin achung chang thudol asei jouse aboljou soh phat un, thingpel chunga kon'in ala lhauvin lhanah alupsah tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 13:29 \xt Matt 27:57-61; Mk 15:42-47; Lk 23:50-56; Jn 19:38-42\x*  
\v 30 Ahivangin Pathen'in thina a kon'in akaithou kittai.  
\v 31 Chuin nikho phabep jouvin Galilee a konna Jerusalem lampia akilhon khompi ho henga ama akiphong in tun amaho Israel mite henga hettohsah in apang uvin ahi.\x + \xo 13:31 \xt Act 1:3\x*  
\v 32 Tunia keiho hiche laiya hi Pathen'in ipu ipateu henga ana kitepna thupha choiya hung kahiuve.\x + \xo 13:32 \xt Labu 2:7\x*  
\v 33 Chule hiche hi ason achilhah eiho jouse henga Pathen'in Jesu akaithou vanga aguilhun sah ahi. Hiche thudol hi Psalm lekhabu nina in hitin aseiyin ahi, “Nangma kachapa, tunin keima napa kahitai.”  
\v 34 Ajeh chu Pathen'in lhana monlha bep ding hilouva thina a konna kaithou dinga ana thutepsa ahi. Pathen'in aseiyin, “David henga kakitepna phattheina kiselguh chu nangma kapeh ding nahi, ati.\x + \xo 13:34 \xt Isa 55:3\x*  
\v 35 Psalm lekhabu dang khat ah ahilchen be in, Na mitheng chu lhan'a namon densah louding ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 13:35 \xt Labu 16:10\x*  
\v 36 Chule hiche thu hi David aseina ahipoi, ajeh chu David chun ama khang sunga Pathen lunggot lam abol jouvin athi in apu apate toh akivui khomin chule atahsa jong amonmang tan ahi.  
\v 37 Ahipoi! Hiche thu hi Pathen'in atahsa monmang louva akaithou midang khat kiseina ahi.  
\v 38 Sopi te ho, ngaiyun! Hiche Jesu vanga chonset ngaidamna aum thudol lhangsama kahiuve.  
\v 39 Koi hijongleh ama tahsan chan chu Pathen anga them changa kisim ding ahi chule hiche hi Mose dan in abol theipoi.  
\v 40 Chingtheiyun! Themgao thusei ho hi nangho chunga chuh sah hih un, ajeh chu ama hon hitin aseiyuve;  
\v 41 “Veuvin mi nuisat ho, kidang sauvin lang thidoh un, ajeh chu nangho phat laiyin thil khat kabolin, hiche thil khat kabol chu mikhat in naheng uva ahung sei jong le na tahsan pouve.” ati.\x + \xo 13:41 \xt Habakkuk 1:5\x*   
\s1 Chidang namdang lah a thusei  
\p
\v 42 Chuin Paul le Barnabas chu kikhopna in'a kon'in apotdoh lhonin ahile mipi chun akham uvin hapta kit le asei lhon jouse avelsei kit lhon dingin angeh un ahi.  
\v 43 Chuin Judah mi tamtah le hougut Judah houva lut mitampi chun Paul le Barnabas chu ajui tauvin ahile amanin amaho chu Pathen milungsetna a umdet jing dingin atilkhou lhon tan ahi.  
\v 44 Chuin ahapta kit in khopi sunga mipi atamjo Pathen thungai dingin ahung khomun ahi.  
\v 45 Ahin Judah mi abang chun mipi chu aveuvin ahile athangse uvin, hijeh chun Paul thusei jouse chu anelkal un ahi.  
\v 46 Chuin Paul le Barnabas chun hangsan tah in alhangsam lhonin asei lhon tai, “Nangho Judah te henga Pathen thu kalhangsap masah lhon ding hi ngaikhoh ahi, ahin nang hon na pampai uva, nangho le nang hon tonsot hinna chang dia lomlouva thu nakitan tah jeh un, chidang namdang te henga kache lhon ding ahitai.  
\v 47 Ajeh chu Pathen'in, ‘vannoi leiset pumpia huhhingna thupole dinga, chidang namdang te lah a vah a kasem lhon nahi,’ atia chu chidang namdang te lah a eisol lhon ahitai,” ati lhon e.\x + \xo 13:47 \xt Isa 42:6; 49:6\x*  
\v 48 Chuin chidang namdang ten hiche thu ajah phat un hapan akipah un Pakai athangvah un chule tonsot hinna chang dinga kilhengdoh ho jouse chu seijui in apang tauvin ahi.  
\v 49 Chuin hiche gamkai sungse achun Pathen thu chu akithe jal tan ahi.  
\v 50 Chuin Judah te chun hougut numei ho le khopi sunga lamkai ho chu atilse uvin Paul le Barnabas chu khopi sunga kon'in adelmang sah tauvin ahi.  
\v 51 Chuin amanin apampai lhon vetsahnan akeng lhona khobon athinglha lhonin Iconium ajon lhon tan ahi.\x + \xo 13:51 \xt Matt 10:14; Mk 6:11; Lk 9:5; 10:11\x*  
\v 52 Chule seijui ho chu kipana le Lhagao vin adimset tauvin ahi.   
\c 14  
\s1 Iconium mun a Paul le Barnabas  
\p
\v 1 Chuin angai ngaiyin Iconium mun'a jong Paul le Barnabas chu Judah te kikhopna insunga alut lhonin thaneitah in thu alhangsam kit lhonin ahile Judah te le chidang namdang mitampin atahsan kit uvin ahi.  
\v 2 Ahinlah Judah te mi konkhat in Pathen thu sang louvin chidang namdang te lungthim sunga Barnabas le Paul dounan thina thei gu akhum peh un ahi.  
\v 3 Ahin solchah teni chu hiche lai mun'a chun sottah aumden lhonin Pakai mi ngailutna thu chu hangsan tah in alhangsam jing lhonin chule athu lhangsap lhon chu atah ahi vetsahna dingin melchihna le bolmo kidang tampi abol lhonin ahi.  
\v 4 Ahinlah hiche khopi sunga miho chu lunggel ni in akihom khen un, konkhat chun Judah te ajop un konkhat ma chun solchah teni thu ajop un ahi.  
\v 5 Chuin chidang namdang mi tamtah le Judah te chun alamkai te hou toh kithon songa se a delkhum ding lung angaito tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin Solchah hon chuche thu ahet lhih phat un Lycaonia gamsunga Lystra le Derbe khopi chule akimvel gamhoa dingin ana jamlut tauvin,  
\v 7 Chule hiche gamsunga chun Kipana Thupha chu asam phong le tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Lystra le Derbe mun a Paul le Barnabas  
\p
\v 8 Chuin Lystra a aumpet un, Paul le Barnabas chun apen apat a akengphang chatmoa lam pumjot theilou mikhat amu lhonin amapa chu atouvin,  
\v 9 Chule Paul thusei chu angaiyin ahi. Chuin Paul in amapa chu ave jangkei in ahile amapa chun damna dinga tahsanna anei chu amutan ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin Paul in aw sangtah in akouvin, “Dingdoh in!” ati. Chuin mipa chu akichomin lam ajot tan ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin mipi chun Paul thilbol chu amu tauvin ahile amaho paovin asam un, “Hiche miteni hi mihem lima um pathen ahi!” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 12 Barnabas chu Greek mite pathen Zeus ahin Paul chun thuseiya pang ahijeh chun Hermes ahi ati tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Chuin Zeus Houbuh chu khopi pamlama umah ahin, Houbuh a natong thempu ho le mipi ho chun bongchal le pahvui khopi kelkot phunga chun ahin pouvin solchah teni ding chun kilhaina agong tauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Ahin solchah Paul le Barnabas in thil umchan thu ajah lhon phat in atija behseh lhonin avon lhon asat eh lhonin mipi lah a kon'in ajam lhon tan, aw sang tah in asam lhonin,  
\v 15 “Golte ho, ipi dinga hitobang hi nabol uham? Keini hi nangho tobanga mihem mai mai kahi lhon bouve! Hiche panna bei thil hoa konna van le leiset, twikhanglen le asunga thil um jouse sempa Pathen hingjing henga nahung lutna thei diuva Kipana Thupha kahin poh lhon ahi bouve.\x + \xo 14:15 \xt Potdohbu 20:11; Labu 146:6\x*  
\v 16 Phat masa lai chun namtin ama ama lung lam cheh a ache theina dingin ana phal in ahi.  
\v 17 Ahin amaho kom'a jong chun Ama hina le aphatna kiphong louvin ana umsah pon ahi. Ajeh chu aman go le dai aphat chan napeuvin anche louhing aphatsah in, nangho dingin neh le chah ning lhingset in napeuvin nalungu kipanan adim in ahi,” ati lhon e.  
\v 18 Thu hicheng aseijou lhon chun amani houna dinga kilhaina bol dinga kigong mipi chu anah nah in akham jou lhonin ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin Antioch le Iconium a kon'in Judah te mi phabep ahung lhungun mipi chu athujo uvin, Paul chu khopi pam lamah akaidoh un songa asep un athitai tin adalha uvin ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin seijui ho avel'a atoukhom pet un Paul chu athoudoh kit in khopi sunga anung lut kit in ahi. Chuin ajingin Barnabas toh Derbe lama dingin achekit lhon tan ahi.   
\s1 Syria gam Antioch mun'a Paul le Barnabas ahung kile  
\p
\v 21 Chuin Derbe a Kipana Thupha alhangsap jou lhon a mi tampi seijuiya asem jou lhon phat in, Paul le Barnabas chu Lystra, Iconium, le Pisidia gam'a Antioch geiyin akile kit lhonin,  
\v 22 Seijui ho asuhat kit lhonin, tahsan na a dingdet jing dingin atilkhou lhonin, chule Pathen Lenggam lutna dinga gentheina le hahsatna tampi athoh ding dan u jong ahetsah lhonin ahi.  
\v 23 Chule Paul le Barnabas chun houbung tin a upa apansah lhonin, chuin upa a apansah lhon ho chu taona le anngol pumin atahsan ngap nau Pakai khut ah apelut tauvin ahi.  
\v 24 Chuin amani Pisidia jotpaiyin Pamphylia chan achekit lhonin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin Perga mun a thu aseijou lhonin Attalia a achesuh kit lhonin ahi.  
\v 26 Achainan, kong in akitol lhonin ahung kipatdoh na lhon Syria gam'a Antioch mun'a akile kit lhon tan ahi. Hiche lai mun'a tahsan chaten Pathen mi ngailutna natoh tongdoh dinga anganse nau atong molso lhon tan ahi.  
\v 27 Chuin Antioch ahung lhun lhon toh kilhonin houbung mipi akou khom lhonin Pathen'in amani a konna thil abol jouse le chidang namdang te dinga jong tahsanna kot ahon dan thudol'a hettohsah lhonin ahi.  
\v 28 Chuin hiche laiya chun seijui ho toh sotpi aumkhom tauvin ahi.   
\c 15  
\s1 Mose thuhil hoa kinel baotam  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Paul le Barnabas Syria gam'a Antioch mun'a aum jing lai lhonin, Judea gam'a kon'in mi phabep ahungun “Mose dan dungjuiya chep natan lou uleh huhhing'a naum theilou dingu ahi,” tin seijui ho chu thu ahung hil'un ahi.\x + \xo 15:1 \xt Thempu Dan 12:3\x*  
\v 2 Chuin Paul le Barnabas chun amaho thuhil chu dih asah lhon lou jeh chun nasatah in akinel tauvin ahi. Ahin achaina channa akihoulhah thei tah loujeh un Houbung chun Paul le Barnabas chu amun houbung mi themkhat toh Jerusalem'a hiche thudoh chung changa solchah ho le upaho toh kihou khom dingin ahin sol tauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Houbung in Jerusalem a dinga ahin sol ho'u chu Phoenicia le Samaria gamsunga akinga pauvin, seijui ho ahin ho pauvin chidang namdang ho lunghei thu chu aseiyun ahile amaho hapan akipah un ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Jerusalem alhun un Barnabas le Paul chu solchah ho le upaho jaonan houbung mipi chun ana lemun, chuin amanin Pathen natoh ho abonchan asei lhon tan ahi.  
\v 5 Ahin Pharisee ho lah a konna seijui ho themkhat ading doh un “Chidang namdang atahsan hon Mose dan dungjuiya chep atanu ngai ahi,” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Solchah ho toh kihou khomna  
\p
\v 6 Chuin solchah ho le upaho chu hiche thua boina ho seilham dingin akikhomun ahi.  
\v 7 Akikhop khom nauva chun, phat sottah akihoulim jouvun Peter ading doh in hitin aseiyin ahi, “Sopi te ho, phat masa a konna Pathen'in nangho lah a konna keima hi chidang namdang ten Kipana Thupha ajah theina dingu le atahsan na ding uva eilhen ahi chu nahe sohkei uve,\x + \xo 15:7 \xt Act 10:1-43\x*  
\v 8 Pathen'in mihem lungthim ahen, eiho eipeh bang uva chidang namdang te jong Lhagao Theng apeh hin Pathen san ahi nau a hettohsah ahi.\x + \xo 15:8 \xt Act 10:44; 2:4\x*  
\v 9 Eiho le amaho kikah a kikhenna asem pon ahi. Ajeh chu aman tahsan na a alungthimu asuhtheng ahitai.  
\v 10 Chuti ahijeh chun, ipi dinga chidang namdang seijui ho chu eiho le ipu ipa teuvin jong anapoh joulou pohgih chu ipohsah uva Pathen ichou dingu ham?  
\v 11 Eiho iboncha uva ichan diuva lomlou Pakai Jesu mingailut vanga huhhing'a um ihiu chu iheuve,” ati.  
\v 12 Chuin Barnabas le Paul in amani jal'a Pathen'in chidang namdang te lah a melchihna leh thil kidang abol thu asei lhon chu mipi chun thipbeh in angaiyun,  
\v 13 Asei jou lhonin, Jacob ading doh in hiti hin aseiyin ahi, “Sopi te ho, ka thusei hi ngaitem uvin,  
\v 14 Chidang namdang te lah a konna Pathen'in ama dinga mi akilah tillai thu chu Peter in aseiya kon'in ija tauve,  
\v 15 Chule hiche chidang namdang te lunghei thudol hi themgao hon ana phondoh masah sau ahitai, ajeh chu hiti hin akisun in ahi.”  
\v 16 “Chujou tengleh kakile kit a, David in lhusa kasem phat a, asesa kasah phat kit a chule kasem phat kit ding ahi.\x + \xo 15:16 \xt Amos 9:11,12\x*  
\v 17 Chutengleh mijouse, chidang namdang te jaona a keima dinga kakou jousen Pakai ahin hol ding ahi tin,  
\v 18 Hitiho jouse phat sottah masanga konna hetsah ji Pakai chun aseiyin ahi.  
\v 19 Chuti ahijeh chun keima thutan chu hiche hi ahi, chidang namdang te Pathen lama lungheina neiho dinga pohgih igot peh lou dingu ahi.  
\v 20 Chusang chun, milim doi anga kikatdohsa anneh, jonthanhoina, hetphah lou saneh, le thisan neh a kon'in kikangse uvin, tin jih thou hite.\x + \xo 15:20 \xt Potdohbu 34:15-17; \xt Thempu Dan 18:6-23; \xt Thempu Dan 17:10-16\x*  
\v 21 Ajeh chu hiche Mose danthu ho hi khopi jouse le cholngah nikho seh a khang tamtah dinga Judah te kikhopna in'a kisei jing ahi.” ati.   
\s1 Thulhuh dungjuiya solchah ho lekhathot  
\p
\v 22 Chuin solchah ho le upahon Jerusalem houbunga kon'in mi phabep alhengdoh un, amaho chu Paul le Barnabas toh Syria gam'a Antioch houbunga akihoulhah nau thu hettohsah dingin asol uvin ahi. Akilheng doh teni chu houbung lamkai Judas (Barsabbas tia jong kihe) le Silas ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin hiche lekhathot hitia kisun hi apohsah un ahi: “Hiche lekhathot hi solchah ho le upaho chule Jerusalem'a um sopiho a kon ahi. Hiche hi Syria gam'a Antioch le Cilicia a um chidang namdang te henga dinga kisun ahi.” Chibai!  
\v 24 “Hichea konna mi phabep in athuhil uva nahung suhboi uva, nahung suh lunghangu chu kaheuve, ahin amaho chu keihon kahin sol u ahipoi!  
\v 25 Hijeh chun kilungkhat tah a kakinopto nau toh lhonin keiho khel in ingailut tah u Barnabas le Paul hi nangho henga kahin sol uvin ahi.  
\v 26 Amani hi Pakai Jesu Christa min'a ahinna chan ngam ahi lhonin ahi.  
\v 27 Chule nahin thudoh chung chang uva kakihou lhah nau hettohsah dinga Judas le Silas hi kahin sol u ahi.”  
\v 28 “Ajeh chu nangho chunga hicheng thil themkhat tailou pohgih poh sahlou ding hi Lhagao Theng leh keiho dinga phajo ahi;  
\v 29 Hicheng thil themkhat ho chu: milim doi anga kikatdohsa anneh, jonthanhoina, het phahlou saneh, le thisan neh a kon'in kikang seuvin, hiche hi najui uva ahileh alhingsel ahitai.”  
\v 30 Chuin thupoho chu Antioch alhunun seijui ho abonun akou khomun hiche lekhathot chu ape tauvin ahi.  
\v 31 Chuin hiche tilkhouna lekhathot chu asimun ahile houbung ho chunga kipana adimset tan ahi.  
\v 32 Chuin Judas le Silas chu ani lhkonna themgao ahi toh lhonin seijui ho tilkhouna le atahsan u suhhatna thu tampi asei lhonin ahi.  
\v 33 Chuin phat chomkhat aum jou lhonin seijui hon amani chu lungmong sel'in Jerusalem houbunga ale sol kit tauvin ahi.  
\v 34 Ahin Silas in chukom'a umden ding ageljo tai.  
\v 35 Paul le Barnabas vang chu Antioch a aum den lhonin, hilaiya chun midang ho toh Pathen thu ahil'un alhangsam un ahi.   
\s1 Paul in Barnabas adalhah, achangseh a che  
\p
\v 36 Phat chomkhat jouvin Paul in Barnabas jah a aseiyin, “Kile kit hitin Pathen thu ilhangsapna khopi jouse chu gavil kit hitin seijui ho iti um hinauvem gave hite,” atin ahi.  
\v 37 Barnabas jong anomin chule John Mark jong puiding anomin ahi.  
\v 38 Ahin John Mark in Pamphylia mun'a ana haisan lhona, natohna a anajao jom tahlou jeh chun ama puikit ding chu Paul akikam khonteh in ahi.\x + \xo 15:38 \xt Act 13:13\x*  
\v 39 Chuphat chun akikhenlo lhonin, Barnabas in John Mark akipuiyin Cyprus lama dingin konga akitol tan ahi.  
\v 40 Paul chun Silas akilhen in, chule tahsan chaten Pakai ngailutna kivoppi dingin asoldoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 41 Chuin Syria le Cilicia gamsungah avahlen houbung ho atilkhou le tan ahi.   
\c 16  
\s1 Timothy, Paul le Silas toh akilhon  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Paul chu Derbe ah ache masan chujouvin Lystra ah achen ahile hikom'a chun seijui khangdong Timothy kiti mikhat anaum'i nahi. Ama chu anu Judah mi ahin, apa vang chu Greek mi ahi.  
\v 2 Timothy chu Lystra le Iconium mun'a angaisang loi tah u seijui khat ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Paul in ama chu alhonpi dingin adeisah in, hijeh chun akilhon khom masang lhonin Judah ten achom mulouna ding uvin Timothy chu chep tanna ding angaiton ahi. Ajeh chu mijousen apa Greek mi ahi chu ahet u ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin amani chu khopi khat a kon'in khopi khat ah avahle lhonin seijui ho chun Jerusalem'a solchah ho le upaho thulhuhna chu phatecha ajui cheh na dingun thu ahille lhon tan ahi.  
\v 5 Chuti chun houbung ho chu atahsan nau suhhat in aumin chule nisih in akhanglen jep jep un ahi.   
\s1 Macedonia mi khat Paul in gao achanna a amu  
\p
\v 6 Chuin Paul le Silas chu Phrygia le Galatia gamsunga akholjin jom lhon tan ahi ajeh chu Lhagao Theng in Asia gamsunga Pathen thulhangsap ding chu ajahda ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin Mysia gamgi ahung lhun lhon phat in Bithynia jon dingin akihei tou lhonin ahile hiche gam'a ache lhon ding jong chu Pakai Lhagao in aphal pon ahi.  
\v 8 Hijeh chun kihei tou talouvin Mysia gamsunga achepeh lhonin Troas kongkaimun chan ache lhon tan ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche ni jan chun Paul in mu aneiyin: Athilmu achun Greece sahlam gam'a um Mecedonia a kon'in mikhat ahung dingin “Mecedonia gam'a hungin lang neihung kithopi uvin,” tin ahung taovin ahi.  
\v 10 Hijeh chun keiho Mecedonia jonin kache tauvin, hiche gam'a Kipana Thupha lhangsam dinga Pathen'in eikouvu ahi chu kahe tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Philippi mun a Paul le Silas  
\p
\v 11 Chuin keiho Troas a kon'in konga katouvun jangjalin kacheuvin Samothrace twikol a kaki ngapa uvin, ajingin Neapolis kalhung tauvin ahi.  
\v 12 Hichea kon chun Mecedonia gamsunga khopi lenloi Rome te khosatna Philippi kalhung tauvin, hichea chun nikho tampi ka nichongun ahi.  
\v 13 Chuin cholngah nikhon khopi pamlama naicha a um vadung panga chun miho taokhom inte tia kagel jeh u chun kacheuvin, hiche mun'a numei phabep anaum khom ho kom'a chun katouvun thu kaseiyun ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin Numei ho lah a chun Lydia kiti Thyatira gammi khat aumin ama chu ponsandup mantam tah a sumkolvei mi ahin chule ama chu Pathen hou jong ahi. Aman ka thuseiju chu phate chan angaiyin ahile Pakaiyin alungthim kot ahin hongin Paul thusei chu ajop tan ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin amanu chu a insung mijouse to baptize achangun, chule amanu'n adongun “Pakai seijui dihtah ahi neitiuva ahile keima in'ah hung lhungun lang kajin in hung pangun,” tin anop tokah uvin angeh tan ahi.   
\s1 Paul in numei khat sunga lhangaoboh anodoh  
\p
\v 16 Nikhat taona ding mun'a kache suh uva ahile lhagao boh vop soh numei khat kamu uvin, amanu chun khonunga hunglhung ding thu aseiya apakai te dinga sum tampipi aloji ahi.  
\v 17 Amanu chun Paul le keiho nung ajuiyin aw sangtah in asamin, “Hiche miho hi Chungnungpen Pathen sohte ahiuvin, chule huhhing'a naum theina dingu thu ahung seiyu ahi,” ati.  
\v 18 Hiti chun nikho tampi abolin ahile Paul jong alunghang tan, chuin akiheiyin asunga cheng lhagao boh kom'a chun aseiyin, “Jesu Christa min'a thu kapeh nahi, amanu sunga kon'in pot in,” atile, apettah chun adalha tan ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin apakaiteu chun haosatna dinga akinepna jouseu ake phat in Paul le Silas amanun kailhang mun'a thunei vaihom ho masanga akailut tauvin,  
\v 20 “Hiche Judah miho jeh hin khopi sung pumpi boina asou sang tai” tin khopi vaihom ho henga asam tauvin ahi.  
\v 21 Chule “Eiho Rome mite chonna toh kitohlou chon dan thu ahilui,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin mipi chu Paul le Silas dounan akikhom uvin, thing tenggol mangcha a ajep theina dingun khopi vaihom ho chun mipi chu thu ape tauvin ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin melse tah a avoh jouvun songkul'a akhumun, songkul ngah ho henga chun phate cha anga tup dingun thu apeuvin ahi.  
\v 24 Hijeh chun songkul ngah hon asung dan langpeh a akeng teni akan khomun akoi tauvin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin jan khangkim laiyin Paul le Silas chu atao lhonin Pathen avahchoi lhonin ahile songkul'a taangho chun angaiyuvin ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin phulou helouvin lingpi nasatah ahung kihot in, songkul khombul ho chu ahin hottan ahile, songkul kot jouse akihong tan, akihen na jouseu jong akilham tan ahi!   
\s1 Philippi mun a songkul tanghon atahsan u  
\p
\v 27 Chuin songkul ngahpa ahung khah doh le songkul kot jouse ana kihon amu phat chun asunga umho jouse jammang gam ahitai tin achem asatdoh in ama le ama akithat kigon ahi.  
\v 28 Ahivangin Paul chun asamin, “Khongaiyin nang le nang kithat hih in! Keiho kabon chauvin kaum nauve!” atin ahi.  
\v 29 Chuin songkul ngahpa chun mei akidet in asungdan langa alhailut in Paul le Silas masanga kithing pum pumin akisep lhutan ahi.  
\v 30 Chuin polama ahin puidoh lhonin, “Pu huhhing'a kaumna dinga ipi kabol ngaiyem?” ati.  
\v 31 Amanin adonbut in “Nang le na insung miten Pakai Jesu tahsanun chutile huhhing'a naum dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 32 Hiti chun ama le a insung mite toh Pathen thu aseikhom tauvin ahi.  
\v 33 Chuin hiche ni jan ma ma chun songkul ngahpa chun akijepna maha lhon chu asop theng peh lhonin, chuin a insung mite jouse toh baptize achang tauvin ahi.  
\v 34 Hiti chun amani ding chun a insunga ankong aluidoh peh un Pathen atahsan jeh u chun a inkouvin akipah lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 35 Ajing jingkah in khopi vaihom ho chun songkul ngahpa henga, “Hiche mite chu soldoh in!” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 36 Chuin songkul ngahpa chun Paul hengah aseiyin, “Khopi vaihom hon nang le Silas soldoh tan atiuvin ahi, hijeh chun lungmong in che lhon tan,” ati.  
\v 37 Ahivangin Paul in adonbut in, “Keini hi Rome mi kahi lhonin kholtoh louva mipi angsunga eivoh u ahin, guhthima eisoldoh got u chu hithei louding ahi. Hijeh chun amaho tah hungu henlang eisoldoh uhen,” ati.  
\v 38 Chuin hiche thu chu khopi vaihom hon ajah doh uva Paul le Silas chu Rome mi ahi ahetdoh phat un,  
\v 39 Songkul'a ahungun amani kom'a chun ngaidam athum tauvin ahi. Chujouvin amani chu apuidoh uvin khopi sung dalha lhon tan tin ataovun ahi.  
\v 40 Chuin Paul le Silas chu songkul'a konna ahung potdoh lhon phat in Lydia in'ah akile kit lhonin hiche in a seijui ho chu atilkhou lhonin chuin amanin khopi chu adalha lhon tan ahi.   
\c 17  
\s1 Thessalonica mun a Paul in thu asei  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Paul le Silas chun Amphipolis le Apollonia khopi ajot peh lhonin Thessalonica ahunglhung lhon tan ahi. Hichea chun Judah te kikhopna in aum'in ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin abolngai bangin Paul chu Judah te kikhopna in'ah cholngah nikho thum kijom in achen Pathen Lekhabu a pansan miho chu akihoulimpi jin,  
\v 3 Miho kom'a chun themgao hon asei banga Messiah chun genthei athoh a chule thina a konna kaithouva aum ding thudol ahilchen jin ahi. Chule “Hiche Jesu athudol kaseipa hi Messiah chu ahi,” atin ahi.  
\v 4 Athusei ngaiho lah a Judah mi phabep le Pathen ging Greek mi chule numei mithupi phabep jaonan Paul le Silas thusei chu ajop uvin amani toh apang khom tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Ahivangin Judah mi loikhat chu athangthip uvin hijeh chun kailhang dunga boina sem ho chu akou khomun mipi atilse uvin, Jason in chu abulhu un, Paul le Silas chu mipi lah a kaidoh dingin ahol uvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin amani amulou phat uvin, Jason le seijui dang phabep chu khopi vaihom ho masanga akaidoh un, chule mipi chun asamun, “Paul le Silas hin vannoi pumpia boina asosah lhon ahin tun eiho khopi sunga jong boina aso lhon tai,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 7 “Hiche thilsoh hi Jason in a-in'a alhunsah jeh ahin, chule ama hon Caesar dounan achonun Jesu kiti leng dang khat aum'e,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 8 Hiche thudol hin Khopi mite le vaihom ho nasatah in alungboi sah tan ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin vaihom ho chun Jason le seijui dang ho chu hunam'in akilhadoh theina dingun man apeh sah un chuin alhadoh tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Berea mun a Paul in thu asei  
\p
\v 10 Hiche ni jan ma ma chun seijui hon Paul le Silas chu Berea a dingin asoldoh tauvin, chuin amani Berea alhun lhon phat in Judah te kikhopna in'ah alutkit lhonin ahi.  
\v 11 Berea mite chu Thessalonica mite sangin alungthim kot u akihong jon, Paul thusei chu lunglut tah in angaiyun ahi. Niseh in Pathen Lekhabu asim jingun Paul le Silas chun thudih asei lhon hinam tin akhol chil un ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche toh kilhon chun Judah mi tampi leh Greek mithupi numei le pasal tampin atahsan tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Ahin Thessalonica a um Judah mi phabep in Paul le Silas in Berea a Pathen thu asei lhon'e ti ahetdoh phat un ahungun mipi atildoh un boina asosah un ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin seijui ho chun thakhat tah in Paul chu twipi gal langkhat ah asoldoh un, Silas le Timothy vang chu aumden lhonin ahi.   
\s1 Athens mun a Paul in thu asei  
\p
\v 15 Paul thah doh a che ho chun Athens kho chanin alhon piuvin, chuin Silas le Timothy jong gangtah a Paul kom alhun lhkonna ding thu ahinpo uvin Berea a ahung kile kit tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Paul in Athens khopi a Silas le Timothy anga sung chun khopi muntin'a milim ho chu amun alungthim ana lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin ama kikhopna in'a alut in, Judah miho le Pathen ging chidang namdang ho toh Pathen thun akihoulim khom uvin, chule niseh in jalhanga jong amuho jouse kom'a aseijin ahi.  
\v 18 Hiti chun Epicurean le Stoic chihgilna nei miho toh akinel'un, chuin Jesu le athodoh chung chang thudol aseiyin ahile, ama hon, “Hiche kamtam pa hin ipi hetkhah lou thukhat asei ham?” atiuvin, amaho lah a konkhat chun, “Hetphah lou pathen thu asei hile akilome,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin ama hon Paul chu khopi vaihom ho anga apuilut un, “Hiche thuhil thah hi keiho kom'a hung seikit in,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 20 “Nangman thil chombeh thu khat naseiyin, hichu keihon kicheh tah in kahet nom uve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 21 (Hiche thuhil thah thudol'a hin Athens mite le gamchoma konna hungkhom miho chun aphatseh in kihoulim nan anei tauvin ahi).  
\v 22 Chuin Paul chu mipi kikhopna a chun ading doh in, hitin aseiyin ahi. “Athens mite ho, nangho hi imalam jousea hougut tah nahiu hi kamudoh in ahi;  
\v 23 Ajeh chu kavahlen ahile pathen kihouna muntheng tampi kamun, hiche maicham phung ho lah a chun ‘hetphah lou Pathen'a ding’ tia kisun khat kamudoh in ahi.” Keiman kasei hi hiche nahet phahlou u Pathen thu chu ahi.  
\v 24 Hiche Pathen chu vannoi leiset le asunga thil um jouse sempa ahin, hijeh chun Ama chu khut a kisa Hou-In'a acheng pon,  
\v 25 Chule mihem khut in angaichat ho apethei pon ahi ajeh chu aman ngaichat aneipoi. Ama chun ahingthei jouse hinna apeh ahin, angai cha jouse ngaichat asuh bulhit pehji ahi.  
\v 26 Aman mihem khat a konna leiset pumpia namtin asemdoh ahin, namkhat hung kitundoh le lhahsuh ding jong aman ahet masah sa ahi, chule agamgi geiya aman adatkhen sa ahi.  
\v 27 Athilsem lona jeh chu namtin in ama ahol'uva amu theina dingu ahi ajeh chu ama eihoa konna gamla tah a umlou ahi.  
\v 28 Ajeh chu eiho ama a ihin uva ama'a ichale theiyuva chule ama'a ihiu ahi. Nangho zaila cheng khat a jong, “Eiho ama chilhah ihiuve” tin akisun in ahi.  
\v 29 Hiti ahijeh chun eihon Pathen chu khutthem hon sana dangka ahilou le songa asemu milim hotoh itelou diu ahi.  
\v 30 “Het louva nabol laiyuva chu Pathen kimumo sah ahin, ahin tua hi hoilai hijongleh mijousen chonset lungheiya ama lam ahin belna dinga thu apeh ahitai.  
\v 31 Ajeh chu aman vannoi thu atan ding nikho atepsa ahin, thudih a thutan ding mikhat apansah in, ama chu mijouse mu din thina a kon'in akai thouvin ahi,” ati.  
\v 32 Chuin Paul in thokit thudol asei chu ajauvin ahileh mi konkhat chun anuisat un, ahin adang ho chun “Hiche thudol hi olleh kangai nom kit-ui,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 33 Hiti chun Paul in akihoulim nau achaiyin ahi.  
\v 34 Ahivangin amaho lah a mi phabep chun atahsan un anung ajui tauvin ahi. Amaho chu, vaipo loiho lah a mi Dionysius, Damaris kiti numeinu chule adang mi phabep ahiuve.   
\c 18  
\s1 Corinth mun a Paul  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Paul chu Athens a kon'in Corinth achetan ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin hikom'a chun Judah mi Aquila chu amun, amapa chu Pontus gam'a peng ahin, Italy gam'a konna Claudius Caesar in Rome a konna Judah te jouse ahin nodoh phat a ajinu Priscilla toh hunglhung til ahi lhone.  
\v 3 Paul chu amaho in'ah alhungin na atong khom jiuvin ahi ajeh chu ama banga pon-in sah them cheh ahiuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Hiti chun cholngah nikho seh le Paul chu kikhopna in'a achen Judah te le Greek mite chu thu ahiljin ahi.  
\v 5 Chuin Silas le Timothy jong Mecedonia a konna ahung suh lhon phat chun Paul in aphat nei jousen Pathen thu alhangsam in, Judah te kom'a Jesu chu Messiah ahi tin asam phong le tan ahi.  
\v 6 Ahin Paul chu adoudal uva alunghan sah jeh un, Paul in aponsil a leivui athing lhan, “Nangho thisan nangho chung ma ma ah chu hen, keima themmona bei kahi, tunia pat a chidang namdang te henga kasap phong ding ahitai,” atin ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin kikhopna inkom'a cheng Pathen ngaisah mi Titius Justus in'ah chun alut tan ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin kikhopna in'a lamkai loi Crispus le a insunga um jouse n Pakai atahsan un, chule Corinth a um midang tamtah in jong Paul thusei chu ajauvin, atahsan un baptize achang tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Jankhat Paul henga Pakaiyin gaovin akimusah in hitin ahin seiyin, “Kicha hih in! Paodoh in! Umthim hih in!  
\v 10 Ajeh chu keiman nangma kaumpi nai, chule hiche khopi sunga hi koiman nabulhu louding nabol gimlou diu ahi, ajeh chu hiche khopi sunga mi tamtah hi keiya ahi,” ati.  
\v 11 Chuin Paul chu Corinth a kum khat le akeh aumden in Pathen thu ahil len ahi.  
\v 12 Ahin Gallio chu Achaia gamvaipoa ahung pan phat in Judah miho chu Paul dounan ahung sousang kit uvin, gamvaipo anga athu tan dingin ahin puiyun,  
\v 13 “Paul in eiho dan toh kikal a Pathen hou dingin mi ajol e,” tin aheh seuvin ahi.  
\v 14 Ahin Paul in akihkonna thu asei toh lhonin Gallio in ahehse ho kom'a chun, “Judah miho, ngaiyuvin, naheh nau thua hi thil dihlou ahilou le thilse ajao khah a ahile naheh nau hi kasanpeh ding nahiuve,  
\v 15 Ahin tun naheh nau thu hi thudoh mai mai, min mai mai, ahilou le Judah te danthu mai mai ahijeh in nang hon kivetsui tauvin, hitobang thu hi katan nompoi,” atin,  
\v 16 Thutanna inna kon'in ahin soldoh tan ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin kikhopna in'a lamkai Sosthenes chu mipi chun aman'un, thutanna inmai laitah a chun avo tauvin ahi. Ahin Gallio chun iman jong agelpeh pouve.   
\s1 Antioch mun a Paul akile  
\p
\v 18 Chujouvin Paul chu Corinth ah phat chomkhat aum'in chuin sopi te ho kom'a lhahna thu aseiyin, akinaipi Cenchrea ajon tan ahi. Hiche laiya chun Paul in Judah te chonna dan dungjuijin akitepna phat alhin phat in asam avoulhan, chuin Priscilla le Aquila toh Syria lam jonin konga akitol tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 18:18 \xt Minbu 6:18\x*  
\v 19 Chuin Ephesus kongkaimun ahung lhun un, hiche laiya chun Paul in amani adalhan ama chu kikhopna inna alut in Juda te chu asuhtoh peh in ahi.  
\v 20 Hichea chun umsot jep dingin ana temun ahin anoppeh pon ahi.  
\v 21 Adalhah ding kon chun, “Pathen lunglam ahile kahung kile kit ding ahi,” tin Ephesus a kon'in konga akitol kit tan ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin Caesarea kongkaimun a akinga kit in, hichea kon chun Jerusalem houbung agavil in chuin Antioch a akile kit tan ahi.  
\v 23 Phat chomkhat Antioch a aum jouvin Paul chu Galatia le Phrygia lama akile kit in, seijui ho akimupi kit in asuhat kit in ahi.   
\s1 Ephesus mun a Apollos thulhangsap  
\p
\v 24 Alangkhat ah, Egypt gam Alexandria a kon'in thusei them tah le Pathen Lekhabu thu hetah Judah mi Apollos chu Ephesus ahunglhung in,  
\v 25 Ama chun Pakai lampi thu ahil in, chule midang ho chu dihtah le Lhagaova thanei tah in Jesu thudol ahil in ahi. Ahinlah ama chun twilutsah John bou ahet ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin kikhopna in'a hangsan tah a thu asei chu Priscilla le Aquila in ajah lhon phat in ama chu akoudoh lhonin Pathen thu kicheh tah in ahilchen be lhonin ahi.  
\v 27 Chuin Apollos in Achaia gam'a che ding lung agel jeh chun sopite hon ama chu atil khouvun, chule Achaia gam'a seijui ho ding chun lekha khat athot un kipah tah a ana lem dingun angeh un ahi. Chuin alhun phat in Pakai mingailut jal'a atahsan ho jouse dinga mi phachom tah asoh tan ahi.  
\v 28 Juda te chu lhang phongin thanei tah in anelkhup jin, Pathen thu dungjuijin, Jesu chu Messiah ahi, tin ahilchen jin ahi.   
\c 19  
\s1 Ephesus mun a Paul  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Apollos Corinth a aum jinglai chun Paul jong chuche gamkai sunga chun avahlen Ephesus ahung lhun chun seijui tampi amun amaho kom'a chun,  
\v 2 “Natahsan uva chu Lhagao Theng nachan nah uvem?” tin adongin ahile, ama hon “Kachang pouve, Lhagao Theng aum'e akiti lam jong kajakha pouve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin aman adong kit in “Ahileh ipia baptize chang nahiuvem?” ati. Ama hon jong “John baptize chanin,” atiuve.  
\v 4 Chuin Paul in, “John baptize chan chu chonsetna a kon lungheina ding bou ahi, ahin John jengin jong miho jah a chun ama jouva hung ding pa chu tahsanun,” ati, hichu Jesu aseina ahi.\x + \xo 19:4 \xt Matt 3:11; Mk 1:4,7,8; Lk 3:4,16; Jn 1:26,27\x*  
\v 5 Chuche thu ajah jah un abonchauvin Pakai Jesu minin baptize achang tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin Paul in achung uva khut angamin ahile, Lhagao Theng achung uva ahung chutan, chule abonchauvin paochom athouvin gaothu asei tauvin ahi.  
\v 7 Amaho chu abonun mi som le ni ahiuve.   
\s1 Judah hon Paul thuhil asanlou u  
\p
\v 8 Chuin Paul chu kikhopna in'ah alut in hapta thum sungin hangsan tah in thu aseiyin, thununsah teina dingin Pathen Lenggam thu ahilin ahi.  
\v 9 Ahin mi konkhat chu alouchal uvin thu kisei chu sang louvin, lhang phongtah in asei seuvin ahi. Hijeh chun Paul in kikhopna in chu adalhan seijui ho chu akipui doh in Tyrannus mun'a thuseina in khat ah niseh in akihoulimpi tan ahi.  
\v 10 Hiti chun kumni jen abol'un ahile Asia gamsung pumpia Judah te le Greek mi abonchauvin Pakai thu chu ajatauvin ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin Pathen'in Paul chu bolmo kidang boltheina tha ape tan ahi.  
\v 12 Chuti chun ultheh pon hihen lang achunga kai pon poupou hijongleh achoiyun adamlou ho chunga akoiyun ahile adamlou nau chu adamin asunga lhagao phalou ho jong ajamdoh jin ahi.   
\s1 Ephesus mun a mi tampin atahsan u  
\p
\v 13 Chuin Judah miho phabep khopi khat a kon'in khopi khat ah avah leuvin, lhagao boh ho anodoh un, amaho chun Pakai Jesu min pat ding agouvin, “Paul in alhangsap Jesu min'a thu kapeh nahi, hungpot in!” tin asei jiuvin ahi.  
\v 14 Hitia thil bol chu thempu lenloi, Sceva chate pasal sagi ho ahiuve.  
\v 15 Ahin chutia nikhat abolgot kit laitah un lhagao boh chun, “Jesu le Paul chu kahenai, nangho koi nahiuvem?” atin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin lhagao boh voppa chu amaho chunga achomlut in amaho chu athajo in asugim tauvin ahile amaho chu sagohkeo le maha pun ajamdoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 17 Hiche thilsoh chu Ephesus khopi sunga Juda te le Greek mite hengah gangtah in akithe jal tan ahile, khopi sungah kichat tijatna adim tan, Pakai Jesu min chu nasatah in ajabol tauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin seijui tamtah ho chun achonset thilbol'u aphong tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin doichoi ho mi tamtah in jong a lekhabu u ahin choikhom uvin, mipi angsung laitah a agouvam tauvin ahi. Hiche alekhabu u chu dangka tamtah man ahi.  
\v 20 Hiche Pakai natoh thudol chu muntin'a akithe jaltan thahat tah in na atong tan ahi.   
\s1 Ephesus mun a thunoh baotam  
\p
\v 21 Chuin phat chomkhat jouvin lhagaovin asoljeh chun Paul chu Jerusalem ache masang'in Mecedonia le Achaia gam'a dingin achen, “Chujou tengleh Rome a kache ding ahi,” tin aseiyin ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin ama Asia gam'a phat chomkhat aum nalaiyin, Timothy le Erastus chu akithopi dingin Mecedonia a amasol in ahi.  
\v 23 Chuche phatlai chun Ephesus ah hiche kithuhilna lampi chung changa boina khohtah khat ahung umdoh tan ahi.  
\v 24 Ajeh chu Demetrius kiti mikhat aumin, ama chu dangka a sumkolvei mi ahin, aman khutthem ho chu dangka in Greek te pathen Artemis lim akhensah in hoitah in akoiyin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin aman anatoh kibahpi ho chu akou khomin ajah uva: “Mipi ho hiche sumkolveina hi ihaodoh nau ahi,” ati.  
\v 26 “Ahin najah uva namu bangun, hiche Paul hin miho jouse kom'a khut a kisem limho hi pathen tahbeh ahipoi tin aseiyin mijouse alhemlha tai, chule hiche thu hi Ephesus khopi bouseh a asei ahipon Asia gamsung pumpia asei le ahi!  
\v 27 Ahinai! Isumkolvei nau mijousen nahsahmoa akoi ding thu bou kasei ahipoi, ahin Artemis pathen houna in thupina jouse aman a, chule Asia gamsung pumpi le vannoi pumpia hiche pathen houna amanthah ding jong hi ka gelkhoh tah khat ahi!” ati.  
\v 28 Hichun akikhom miho chu alunghang jah jeng uvin, “Ephesus mite pathen Artemis alen'e,” tin hasap in asam tauvin ahi.  
\v 29 Hichun khopi sunga miho chu alung boilah lah jeng uvin, mipi chun Paul hin kilhonpi Macedonia gam'a kon Gaius le Aristarchus chu amanun golseh vetna mun'a chun akailut tauvin ahi.  
\v 30 Chuin Paul jong chun lut ding agon, ahin seijui hon ana lutsah pouvin ahi.  
\v 31 Chuin Asia gamsung a Paul loi le gol milen milal phabep in Paul henga thu ahin thot un, golseh vetna mun'a lut loubeh dingin ahung taovun ahi.  
\v 32 Golseh vetna mun sunga chun mipi chu apeng lah lah un mi abangin thil khat asamun, abangin thil dang khat asamun, hiti chun aeu lah lah jeng uvin, abangloi chun ipi jeh a kikhom ahiu jong ahepouvin ahi.  
\v 33 Chuin mipi lah a um Juda miho chun Alexander chu mipi masanga ahin sondoh un thilsoh thudol ahilchet dingin asolun ahi. Chuin aman mipi ho chu aphoh thip in houlim ding agon ahi.  
\v 34 Ahinlah mipi ho chun amapa chu Juda mi ahi ahetdoh phat un, hatah in asamkit un, “Ephesus Artemis alen e, Ephesus Artemis alen e!” tin nidan ni lang asamun ahi.  
\v 35 Ajo jonan khopi vaipopa chun mipi ho chu aphoh thip in aman, “Vo Ephesus mite, Ephesus khopi hi van'a konna hung khelha Artemis len lim hou-in ngah ahi hi mijousen ahet ahi,” ati.  
\v 36 “Hiche thutah hi koiman aseilep theilou ahijeh in nangho thipkhen chan um unlang imacha kinothe thun bol dauvin.  
\v 37 Hiche napuilut u mite hin hou-in'a kon'in imacha agudoh pouvin, eiho pathen dounan jong ima asei pouve.  
\v 38 Amavang Demetrius le anatoh kibahpi khutthem hon amaho hehsetna ding thu aneiyuva ahile thutanna in honsan aum jinge, chule gamvaipo ho henga jong athu agasei theiyu ahi. Amaho kom'a khun ga kiheh sah tauvin.  
\v 39 Chule ahehnau thudang aum le vang angaiya kikhopna in'a athu tan ding ahi.  
\v 40 Ajeh beiya boina soh ahijeh in ajole Rome vaipo ten ichung uva thu ahin tan khah diu ham tin kichat nan kadime. Ajeh chu Rome vaipo ten tuni thilsoh thudol hilchen dingin eihin dongule ima isei theilou diu ahi,” ati.  
\v 41 Hiti chun mipi ho chu anodoh tan ahile amaho akikhen tauvin ahi.   
\c 20  
\s1 Macedonia gam a Paul kholjin  
\p
\v 1 Chuin mipi sousang na chu athip phat in Paul in seijui ho chu agakousah in atilkhou jouvin, damselun tin akikhen pin ama Macedonia lamah achetan ahi.  
\v 2 Chuche gamsunga ajotpa na khopi jousea seijui ho atilkhou peh in chuin Greece khopi chanin achesuh tan ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin hiche khopia chun lhathum sung aumin, Syria gam lama konga kinung tol ding angaiton ahile Juda mi phabep in tha ding agot u ahetdoh phat in Macedonia lang joh jotpa dingin akile kit tan ahi  
\v 4 Ama chu mi phabep toh alhonin ahi. Amaho chu: Berea a kon Pyrrhus chapa Sopater, Thessalonica a kon Aristarchus le Secundus, Derbe a kon Gaius, Timothy, chule Asia gam'a konna Tychicus le Trophimus ahiuve.  
\v 5 Amaho chu ana masauvin Troas mun'a eina ngah un ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin Kalchuh Kut kichaijin Macedonia gam'a Philippi khopia kon'in konga katouvun ni nga jouvin Troas mun'a amaho heng kalhung uvin, chuin hiche mun achun hapta khat kaumun ahi.   
\ms1 Troas mun a Eutychus kikaithou  
\p
\v 7 Chuin nimasa nin seijui ho toh Pakai Anjon jong dingin kakikhomun hichea chun Paul in amaho henga thu aseiyin, ajinga ama chekit ding ahitah jeh chun jankim chan ahoulimin ahi.  
\v 8 Hiche kakikhop nau indan chungnunga chu meivah tamtah kide ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin Paul in phat sottah thu asei jeh chun bangkot kom'a tou gollhang chapang khat amin Eutychus atiu chu aihmutso beh seh jeh chun aihmulhu tan ahile bangkot a kon chun in danthum a sanga chun akileh lhan noilama athisa in aga muvin ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin Paul akumsuh in abungin akhut in hiche gollhang chapang pa chu apomin, “lungdong hih un ahing nalaiye” ati.  
\v 11 Chuin amaho indan chungnunga akaltou kit un Pakai Anjon changlhah aneuvin ahi. Hiti chun Paul in thusei abanjom kit in khovah lhah phat in aman adalha tauvin ahi.  
\v 12 Alangkhat ah gollhang chapang pa jong chu aki suhkhahna beihel in inlam'a akilen ahileh mijouse chu alungmong lheh jengun ahi.   
\s1 Troas a pat Miletus chan Paul konga akitol  
\p
\v 13 Chuin Paul chu Assos chanin keng lamah ana chepeh in, keiho konga kacheuva chule ama kalahpana diuva agontoh ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin hiche mun'a kon chun ama jong keiho toh konga katou khomun Mitylene chan ka cheuvin ahi.  
\v 15 Ajingin Kios twikol ka khokhel un, akit in Samos twikol kajot paikit un chule nikhat jouvin Miletus twikol kalhung uvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Asia gamsunga aumsot nomlou phat in Paul in konga touva Ephesus khopi jotpai ding lung angaito tan ahi. Kinotah a cheloiya ahithei le Pentecost masanga Jerusalem lhun tei ding ati ahi.   
\s1 Paul in Ephesus upaho availhah  
\p
\v 17 Ahin Miletus kalhun un Ephesus Houbung a um upaho henga ahung kimupi diuvin thu athot tan ahi.  
\v 18 Chuin amaho ahung lhun phat un aman “Nanghon naheuve, Asia gamsung kahung chotlut nikhoa pat tuni chanin,  
\v 19 Kineosah tah le mitlhi pumin Pakai na katongin, Juda te a konna gimbolna tamtah jong kathoh in ahi.  
\v 20 Chule nangho jah ding imacha imlouvin, japi lah le intin'ah kahil leuvin ahi.  
\v 21 Juda te le Greek te henga thukhat seh hichu, chonsetna a kon lungheiya chule Pathen lama kiheiya, chule Pakai Jesu tahsan ding thu bou chu kasei jing ahi.  
\v 22 Tun keima Lhagaovin Jerusalem'a che dingin eisom tan, ipin einga ham jong kahepoi.  
\v 23 Khopi tin a Lhagao Theng in eihetsah bangin thohgimna le songkul tanna tailou ima kahepoi.  
\v 24 Ahin ka hinkho hi Pakai Jesun eingansena banga midang te henga Pathen mi ngailutna kidangtah Kipana Thupha sap phongna natohna a ka manchah loule thil dang amanna ding kahepoi.\x + \xo 20:24 \xt 2 Tim 4:7\x*  
\v 25 Chule tunia Pathen Lenggam thudol ka seipeh miho hin keima eimukit tah lou diu ahi.  
\v 26 Tu nikhoa hi ka phondoh ahi, keiman kitah tah a ka seipeh nahiuvin nalah uva koi tobang khat tonsot thina toh aum khah a ahile keima thepmo ahi tapoi.  
\v 27 Ajeh chu Pathen'in nangho hetsah dinga adeisah jouse imlouhel a ka seipeh nahi tauve.  
\v 28 Chule tun, chingtheiyun, nang hon Pathen kelngoi hon, athisan'a achohdoh houbung, chu vah unlang chingtup un, hiche dinga chu Lhagao Theng in upa a napansah u ahi.  
\v 29 Ajeh chu kadalhah tengu le nangho lah a konna ngeihang tobang thuhillhem hunglut a kelngoi ho hi khatcha ahin hoilou ding kahei.  
\v 30 Chule nangho lah jenga jong hi mi phabep in amaho thu ahinjop a thutah chu akaleh a ahin hil dingu ahi.  
\v 31 Hijeh chun nangho kiging phauvin! Kumthum sunga asun ajana mitlhi tamtah puma kaumpiu chu geldoh jingun.  
\v 32 Chule tunia hi keiman nangho hi Pathen le ami ngailutna thu alhenchomte toh goulo khom dinga natungdoh theiyu thua chu kanganse nahiuve.  
\v 33 Keiman koima dangka le Sana chule nihchen ponsil hoi ka otcha poi.  
\v 34 Ajeh chu kakhut a konna keima ngaichat le kaum khompi ho ngaichat ding katoh a kakivah ahi.  
\v 35 Chule na hatoh a toh'a migenthei ho kithopi ding dan keima tah hinkhoa namu u ahitai. Pakai Jesun ‘Akisan ho sanga apeho nunnom jo ahi’ ati chu geldoh jingun.”  
\v 36 Chuin thu asei jouvin adilsun amaho toh ataokhomun ahi.  
\v 37 Amaho abonchauvin akap un akikoiyun damselin, tin akikhen tauvin ahi.  
\v 38 Neimu kit tah lou diu ahi ati jeh chun amaho abonchauvin lungngui tah in ama chu kong mun'a agathah tauvin ahi.   
\ms1 Tyre mun a Paul  
\c 21  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Ephesus houbung upaho henga lhahna thu asei jouvin, Cos twikol jonin konga kakitolun, ajingin Rhodes kalhungun chule chua kon chun Patara kajonun ahi.  
\v 2 Chua kon chun Phoenicia jon ding kong khat ah katoudoh un,  
\v 3 Chule Cyprus twikol chu kagalmu phat un, veilama kakiheiyun Syria gam'a Tyre kongkaimun ah kakinga uvin hichea chun konga thil ho chu asolhauvin ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin vapam achun kavah leuvin ahile seijui phabep kaga mudoh un, amaho kom'a chun hapta khat kaumun ahi. Hichea seijui ho chun Lhagao Thenga kon'in gaothu aseiyun, Paul chu Jerusalem'a chejom lou dingin aseiyun ahi.  
\v 5 Chuin hapta kichaiya konga kanung kaldoh ding phat un, mipi jouse, numei chapang jaonan, khopi sunga kon'in vapam chan'ah ahung kumsuh un, hichea chun, dilsun kataovun,  
\v 6 Chule lhahna thu kaseiyun chuin keiho konga toudoh dingin ka cheuvin, amaho jong inlam cheh a akile tauvin ahi.  
\v 7 Tyre kadalhah jou uva ka kingah nau masapen chu Ptolemais ahi. Hichea chun sopi numei le pasal ho chibai kaboh pauvin amaho henga chun nikhat kakibangpa uvin ahi.   
\s1 Caesarea mun a Paul  
\p
\v 8 Ajingin Caesarea lamah kache paiyun, anhom ledinga mi sagi kilhengdoh ho lah a mikhat Kipana Thupha lhangsam Philip in'a chun kalhung tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 21:8 \xt Act 6:5; 8:5\x*  
\v 9 Amapa chun chanu jinei lou li aneiyin amaho chu abonun Lhagao thilpeh gaothu seina achangun ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin nikho tamtah jouvin Lhagao thilpeh gaothu seina chang Agabus kiti mikhat, Judea gam'a kon'in ahungin.\x + \xo 21:10 \xt Act 11:28\x*  
\v 11 Paul konggah chu alan, ama khut le keng chu asomin, “Lhagao Theng in aphondoh ahi, hiche konggah neipa hi Jerusalem'a Juda te lamkai hon amat uva chidang namdang te henga apeh doh dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 12 Chuin hiche gaothusei kajah phatun keiho le amun a um seijui hon Paul henga Jerusalem ache louna dingin kataovun ahi.  
\v 13 Ahinlah Paul in aseiyin, “Ipi dinga kap nahiuvem? Kalungthim nasujun uve! Keima chea songkul tan ding mai mai hilouvin Pakai Jesu min a thi dinga jong gotsa kahitai,” ati.  
\v 14 Chuin keihon kahet chet phat un imacha kaseibe tapouvin, “Pakai lunglam himaihen,” katiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Jerusalem mun a Paul  
\p
\v 15 Chujouvin kathil ho'u kagong tup un Jerusalem'a dingin kache tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Caesarea a kon'in seijui phabep in eilhonpi uvin, chuin Cyprus gammi seijui masaloi Mnason in'ah eipui lut un ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin Jerusalem kalhun un amun a um sopi numei le pasal hon phate chan eina vailhunun ahi.  
\v 18 Ajingin Paul jong Jacob toh kimuto dingin keiho toh kalhonun, hichea chun Jerusalem houbung upaho jouse jong aumun ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin chibai aboh jouvun Paul in Pathen'in chidang namdang te chunga kidangtah a na atoh ho abonchan aseitan ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin Paul thusei ajah phat un Pathen avahchoiyun ahi. Chule ama hon aseiyun “Ngailut umtah sopipa Juda mi sang tamtah in jong atahsan uva chule Mose dan jong phatecha ajui uhi nahet em?  
\v 21 Ahinlah Jerusalem'a Judami atahsan ho hin, nangman chidang namdang te lah a cheng Juda mi seijui hon Mose dan anungsun dingun thu nahil e ti ajauvin, achateu chep atanlou diu chule chonna dan adang dang jong ajuilou diuvin thu nahil e ti aheuvin ahi.  
\v 22 Nangma nahung hila ahet tei ding'u ahin, ipi ilo diu hitam? Atiuvin ahi.  
\v 23 Hijeh chun hiche nabol ding hi pha kasauve. Hichea hin kitepna neijou mili aumun, aluchang'u kivotol dinga kigong ahiuve.\x + \xo 21:23 \xt Minbu 6:13-21\x*  
\v 24 Amaho toh hin lhonin lang Hou-In a gakisutheng unlang, chonna dan dungjuiya sam avona dingun seipeh in, chutile mihon athujah jouseu hi alhem ahin, chule nangma tah jengin jong Juda te dan ajuinai tihi ahetdoh dingu ahi.  
\v 25 Chidang namdang seijui te vang chu lekhathot a isei jouseu banga chon dingu ahi. Milim anga kikatdohsa an anehlou dingu, thisan ahilou le hetlou sa anehlou dingu, chule jonthanhoina a konna kikangse dingu ahi,” atiuve.\x + \xo 21:25 \xt Act 15:29\x*  
\v 26 Chuin Paul chu ajingin hiche mili ho toh chun Hou-In a acheuvin, kisuhtheng na achelhahpi un, chule mipi angsunga chun phongtah in kisuhthengna nikho kichaini ding le amichan cheh a kilhaina abol diu thu aseiyin ahi.   
\s1 Paul amat u  
\p
\v 27 Chuin nisagi kichai kon'in Asia gam'a konna Juda mi phabep in Hou-In sunga Paul amudoh phat un, mipi chu atilseuvin aman tauvin ahi.  
\v 28 Chuin ama hon aseiyun, “Israel mite nei kithopiuvin! Hiche mipa hin muntin'a eiho dounan thu asei jingin, chule mijouse kom'a Juda te chonna dan ajui louna dingun thu aseiye. Hou-In dounan thu aseiyin, chule Hou-In jenga jong chidang namdang te ahin puilut in asuboh in ahi” atiuve.  
\v 29 (Ajeh chu hiche masang jep a chu Paul chu khopi sunga Ephesus mi Trophimus toh amu thau ahi. Paul chun hiche mipa chu Hou-In'ah puilut teiyinte tia agelu ahi.)\x + \xo 21:29 \xt Act 20:4\x*  
\v 30 Chuin hiche ahehset nau hin khopi sung chu ahotling tan, chule boina asousang tan ahi. Chuin Paul chu Hou-In'a kon'in gangtah in akaidoh un kelkot akhah chah tauvin ahi.  
\v 31 Chutia Paul tha ding agot laiyun, Jerusalem mite asousang thu chu Rome sepaite vaipi popa heng alhung tan ahi.  
\v 32 Gangtah in asepai ho leh alamkaiho toh mipi lah a chun achesuh tauvin ahi. Chuin mipi chun sepai vaipi popa le asepai ho hung kumsuh chu amu phat un Paul avoh u chu anga tauvin ahi.  
\v 33 Chuin vaipipo chun Paul chu akan'in, thihkhao nia hen dingin thu apen, chuin mipi ho kom'a chun hiche mipa hi koi ham chule ipi abolset ham tin adong tan ahi.  
\v 34 Chuin mi abangkhat in thil khat asamin, chule abangkhat chun thil dang khat ma asamun ahi. Chutia mipi eu jeh le kicheh loujeh chun ima thudih ahedoh thei tapon, hijeh chun Paul chu kulpi sunga apuilut ding'un thu apetan ahi.  
\v 35 Chuin Paul chu kulpi sung alut kigon ahile mipi ho jeh chun alut thei tapon hijeh chun ama ventupna dingin sepai hon alengkouvun aput thouvin ahi.  
\v 36 Chuin mipi ho chun anung ajuiyun “Thatdoh un, thatdoh un,” tin asamun ahi.  
\v 37 Chuin Paul kulpi sung alhut ding konun, vaipipo kom'a ataovin, “Nakom'a thu khat kasei thei ding ham? ati. Chuin vaipipo chun kidang satah in Greek pao nahet em, tin adongin ahi.  
\v 38 Nangma Egypt mi, masang laiya miho tilsea mi sangli gamthip a loidoh pa chu nahi louham?” ati.  
\v 39 Paul in adonbut in “Kahipoi, keima Tarsus gam'a khopi thupi tah Cilicia a kon Judah mi kahi bouve amaho toh hin nei kihousah in,” atin ahi.  
\v 40 Chuin vaipipo chun anoppeh jeh chun, Paul chu kalbi a chun adingin mipi ho chu thipbeh a um dingin atemin, chuin mipi thipchet a aum phat in amaho pao Aramaic in ahoulimin ahi.   
\ms1 Paul in ama kihkonna a thu asei  
\c 22  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Paul in, “Sopite le jaumtah pate ho, kakihkonna thu kasei hi ngaiyuvin,”  
\v 2 Amaho paova thu asei chu ajah phat un mipi ho chu athipchet jengun,  
\v 3 Chuin Paul in, “Keima Tarsus gam'a Cilicia khopia peng Juda mi kahin, chule chihna thepna lama Jerusalem'a Gamaliel noiya hung seilen kahi. Ama noiya hung seilen khat kahi jeh chun Juda te dan le chonna ho phatecha hung kijil kahi. Tunia nangho jouse banga hi Pathen a dinga tompan tah mi kana hin ahi.\x + \xo 22:3 \xt Act 5:34-39\x*  
\v 4 Chule anungjui ho ka sugentheiyin, abang kathat jin, chule numei pasal kamanin songkul'ah kakhum jin ahi.\x + \xo 22:4 \xt Act 8:3; 26:9-11\x*  
\v 5 Thempu Chungnung le kivaihomna upahon hiche hi eihetpeh u ahi. Ajeh chu Damascus a um sopi Juda te henga kahunga Christian ho kamat a suhgenthei dinga Jerusalem'a kahin kaina dinga amaho kom'a phalna lekha kahin kichoi ahi.”  
\v 6 Ahin Damascus khopi lut ding kon lampi laitah ah, hichu sunkim ahin, hichun van'a kon'in vah hattah khat in kakimvel ahin kho tan,  
\v 7 Keijong tol'a kalhu jengin ahile aw khat kajan, “Saul, Saul, ipi dinga nei bolset jing ham?” ahin tin ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin ken jong, “Nang koi nahim?” kati. Chuin aw chun eihin donbut in 'Keima nabolset jing Nazareth Jesu chu kahi' ahin tin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin kakilhonpi miho chun vah chu amuvin, ahin kakom'a thusei aw chun ipi asei ham ahe pouve.  
\v 10 Hichun “Ipi kabol ding ham Pakai” tin kadongin ahile, Pakaiyin eihin donbut in 'Thoudoh inlang Damascus khosunga khun lut in chuteng ipi nabol ding nakisei peh ding ahi,' ati.  
\v 11 Vah hattah jeh a kamit in kho amutah lou jeh in kalhonpi ho chun kakhut in eikaiyun khopi sunga eikailut un ahi.  
\v 12 Hichea chun Ananias ana chengin ama chu Pathen gingtah mi ahin Juda te dan juithem tah le Damascus khopia um Juda te jousen angaisang tah mi khat ahi.  
\v 13 Ama chu kakom'a ahung dingin, “Sopipa Saul, kho mukit tan atin ahile apettah chun ama chu kamu tan ahi.”  
\v 14 Chuin aman, “Ipu ipateu Pathen chun alunggot lam heding le, dihtah pa mua, chule athu ngai dinga nalhen ahitai” ati.  
\v 15 Ajeh chu nangman namu ho leh najah ho jouse chu nasei phong le-a ama thu hettohsah a napan ding ahitai.  
\v 16 Ipi na khongai nahlai ham? Kipatdoh in lang baptize chang tan, Pakai min kouvin lang na chonset soplhan eiti.  
\v 17 Chuin Jerusalem kahung kile chun Hou-In ah dilsun kataovin ahile,  
\v 18 Gaovin Jesu kamun aman, 'Kipat loiyin! Jerusalem'a kon'in jamdoh in ajeh chu hiche laiya miho hin keima thudol'a nathusei asanlou dingu ahi' ati.  
\v 19 Ahin keiman kaseiyin, “Pakai kikhopna in tin a seijuiho kasuh gentheiya songkul'a kakhum jong ahe sohkei uve”  
\v 20 Chule nasohpa Stephen aselih pet uva asangkhol sutlhah hou akoinau kom'a ding jong chu kana hinai, kati.\x + \xo 22:20 \xt Act 7:58\x*  
\v 21 Ahin Pakaiyin, 'Chen, gamla tah a chidang namdang te lah a kasol ding nahi!' ati.   
\s1 Rome sepai kaidongpa in mun a Paul  
\p
\v 22 Hichun mipi hon chuche Paul thusei chu ajah phat un asam uvin, “Hitobang mi chu delmang un, ahing dinga jong lom ahipoi!” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin mipi chun asangkhol u asut un, vanlama vutvai atheuvin ahi.  
\v 24 Chuin Sepai vaipopa chun, Paul chu inpi sunga apuilut sah in, mipi achunga chubang tah a alunghan nau ajeh seidoh sah ding ngaito nan jepsah dingin thu apetan ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin Paul chu jep dinga ahin kan phat un aman akom'a ding sepai lamkaipa henga chun, “Rome mikhat athemmona khol masa louva jep ding chu dan in aphal hinam?” tin adongin ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin sepai lamkai pan chuche ajah phat chun sepai vaipopa kom'a achen, “Ipi bol nahim? Ama hi Rome mi hibouva hila!” atin ahi.  
\v 27 Chuin sepai vaipopa chu Paul henga ahungin, “Nangma Rome mi nahim? seiyin,” tin adong tan ahile Paul in jong “Kahinai,” ati.  
\v 28 Chuin sepai vaipopa chun aseiyin “Kei jong sum tampi kapeh jouva Rome mihina chang kahi bouve,” atin ahile Paul in “Keivang kapen apat a Rome mi a peng kahi,” ati.  
\v 29 Chuin Paul in Rome mi kahi ati ajahdoh phat in thudong dinga kigong sepai ho chu gang tah in apotdoh tauvin ahi, chule sepai vaipopa jong chun chutobang thupeh anei jeh chun akicha lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 30 Ajing nikhon Paul chung changa boina thu hetdohna dingin sepai vaipopa chun Juda te kivaihom na a lamkaiho leh thempu ho chu hungkhom dingin thu apen, chule amaho masanga ding dingin Paul chu ana lhadoh tan ahi.   
\c 23  
\s1 Lamkai ho kikhopna mun a Paul  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Paul in houvaipo ho chu ave changmel in, “Sopi te ho, Pathen angsunga se le pha hetkhen na kicheh tah neiya hingjing kahi!”  
\v 2 Chuin Thempu Chungnung Ananias chun Paul toh kinaiya umho kom'a chun amuhsom abehpeh dingun thu apen ahi.  
\v 3 Ahin Paul in, “Phat louna a dim miphalhem pa! Pathen'in nangma nabeh ding ahi, itobang thutan mi nahiya nangman dan napal keh a chutobang a eibeng dinga mi thu napeh ham?” ati.\x + \xo 23:3 \xt Matt 23:27,28\x*  
\v 4 Chuin Paul kimvela ding ho chun, “Pathen Thempu Chungnung chu na housal ngam ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 5 Paul in adonbut un, “Sopi te ho, neingai damun, Thempu Chungnung ahilam kana hetlou ahi, ajeh chu Pathen Lekhabun ‘nalamkai te chunga thuse nasei louding ahi’ tin akisune” ati.\x + \xo 23:5 \xt Potdohbu 22:28\x*  
\v 6 Chuin Paul in hou vaipoloi ho kikhopna a chu Sadducee ho leh Pharisee ho kihal ahiu ahet doh phat chun, hatah in asamin, “Sopi te ho, kapu kapate khanga pat a Pharisee mi kahin! Thokit thudol'a kinepna kanei jeh a kachung thu kitan ahi!” atin ahi.\x + \xo 23:6 \xt Act 26:5; Philp 3:5\x*  
\v 7 Hijeh chun Pharisee ho le Sadducee ho chu hopnin aki homkhen tauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Ajeh chu Sadducee ho chun mihem thokitna, vantil, chule lhagao um thudol atahsan lou u ahi, ahin Pharisee ho vang chun aboncha a hi atahsan u ahi.\x + \xo 23:8 \xt Matt 22:23; Mk 12:18; Lk 20:27\x*  
\v 9 Chuin akah uva boina asousang tan, houdan thuhil'a pang Pharisee phabep chun thunei tah in, “Hiche pa chunga hin thildih lou ima aumpoi, lhagao ahilou le vantil in ahenga thu asei hitei ding ahi,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin akah uva kitomona asan cheh cheh phat in sepai vaipopa chun Paul chu kehni sokhauvin te tin, sepai ho chu asollin Paul chu hunam in aga huhdoh sah in kulpi sunga apuilut sah tan ahi.  
\v 11 Hiche ni jan chun Paul henga Pakai akilah in, “Paul, lungneo hih in. Hiche Jerusalem'a keima nei phondoh banga hi, Rome a jong Kipana Thupha hettohsah a napan ding ahi” ati.   
\s1 Judah ho phabep in Paul hinkho suhbeina ding agon u  
\p
\v 12 Ajing jingkah in Juda miho phabep akiloiyun Paul itha tokah uva an ineh lou diu ahi tin akihahsel tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Chutia kigahna sem chu abonun mi somli aval uvin ahi.  
\v 14 Chuin amaho thempulen ho leh upaho henga acheuvin aga seiyuvin, “Paul katha tokah uva ima nelou dinga kihahsel kahiuve,” aga tiuvin ahi.  
\v 15 “Hijeh chun nangho vaipo hon sepai vaipopa henga gaseiyun lang Paul chu achung chang thudol kholchet be dingin houvaipo ho anga hin nung puikit in tin gathum uvin, chutengleh keihon ama chu lamkah a katha diu ahi,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Ahin hiche tohgon chu Paul sopinu chapan ajah lhih phat in kulpi sunga alhailut jelin Paul henga agasei tan ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin Paul in Rome sepai jalamkai khat akouvin, “Hiche khangdong pa hi sepai vaipi popa henga puilut uvin ajeh chu sei ding thupitah khat aneiye,” ati.  
\v 18 Chuin Sepai jalamkai pa chun aseiyin, “Songkul'a um Paul chun eikouvin, hiche khangdong pa hin sepai vaipipo henga seiding thupitah aneiye atin eihin puilut sah ahi,” atin ahi.  
\v 19 Chuin sepai vaipipo chun akhut in atuh in, “Ipi ham nasei nom chu?” tin adong tan ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin Paul sopinu chapa chun, “Jing nikho tengleh Juda mi phabep in hou vaipoloi anga dinsah kit dinga nahenga konna achungthu kholbe ding kisa a Paul ahung puidoh got diu ahi.  
\v 21 Ahin soldoh hih in ajeh chu mi somli valin lamkah a chanlhih a chuleh atha tokah uva ima nelou dingin akihahsel uve, chule tua hi nangma thulhuh bou angau ahitai,” tin asei tan ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin sepai vaipipo chun khangdong pa henga, “Keima kom'a hiche thu nahung sei hi koima hetsah hih in,” tin agihsal tan ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin sepai vaipipo chun sepai jalamkai ni akouvin “Tujan nidan ko tengleh Caesarea jon dingin sepai jani gotsan koi lhonin, chule tengchoi sepai jani le sakol sepai somsagi jong gong tup lhonin.  
\v 24 Chule Paul touna ding sakol khat jong gong lhonin lang gamvaipo Felix henga kitup selin gathah un,” atin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin gamvaipo ding chun lekha khat ajih in,  
\v 26 “Jaumtah gamvaipo Felix, Claudius Lysias a kon'in salam!” tin athot in ahi.  
\v 27 “Hiche pa hi Juda ten abulhu uva tha dinga anagot pettah un sepai hotoh kagalut un, Rome mi ahi kahetdoh phat in bitkeiyin kahin huhdoh e.  
\v 28 Chuin ahehset nau hetdohna dingin hou vaipoloi angsunga kadinsah in ahileh,  
\v 29 Aheh nau hi amaho houthu toh kisai ahi kahedoh tan, ima songkul tanna ding le thana ding kamupon ahi.  
\v 30 Ahin tha dinga agot u kahet doh phat a apet pet a nahenga kahin sol ahitai, chule ahehse ho jong nangma henga hung dingin ka seipeh tauve,” ati.  
\v 31 Thupeh dungjuijin sepai hon Paul chu Antipatris heng alhut un ahi.  
\v 32 Ajing jingkah in amaho ahung kinung leuvin ahin sakol sepai hon Paul chu Caesarea chan aga thah un ahi.  
\v 33 Chuin Caesarea alhun un Paul le Lekhathot chu gamvaipo Felix henga apelut tauvin ahi.  
\v 34 Chuin lekhathot chu asim jouvin Paul chu “hoilai gamkai mi nahim” tin adongin ahileh Paul in “Cilicia,” ati.  
\v 35 Chuin gamvaipo chun, “Na hehse ho ahung lhun teng nachung thu kakhol ding ahi,” atin chujouvin gamvaipo chun Herod inpia songkul'a koi dingin thu apetan ahi.   
\c 24  
\s1 Gamvaipo Felix anga Paul  
\p
\v 1 Chuin ni nga jouvin gamvaipo henga Paul ahehset nau thusei dingin Thempu Chungnung Ananias le Juda te upa phabep chule Tertullus kiti minelkal them chu ahunglhung tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin Paul chu ahin puilut uvin ahile Tertullus chun gamvaipo henga Paul hehna thu hitin ahin seitan ahi: “Nangma vaihom themna le nangma jal'a keiho Juda te hi phat sottah lungmonga um kahiuve.”  
\v 3 “O Lal chungnung, hiche ho jeh hin keiho kakipah lheh jeng uve.  
\v 4 Ahin nangma kalungjin sah nompoi hijeh chun nei lungset inlang phat chom chakhat neingai peh in tia kahung tao ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche pa hi phatseh a Juda te umna jousea boina semjing kei mi ahi kamudoh un, chule thuhillhem Nazareth Jesu chon a chon ho lamkai pipu ahi ti kamudoh uve.  
\v 6 Chukit jong le kamat uva chu aman Hou-In jong suhboh ding agot ahi.  
\v 7 Keihon keiho dan dungjuiya athu katan got u ahin, hinlah sepai jalamkai Lysias in thahat san'a kakhut uva konna ahung puidoh ahi.  
\v 8 Kaheh nau hi nangma tah in dong lechun adihtah chu namat doh ding ahi,” atin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin Judah mi adang ho jong chun Tertullus in asei jouse adih ahi atiuvin ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin gamvaipo chun Paul jong thu asei sah in, chuin Paul in, “Pu, kum tamtah Juda te chunga thutan'a hung pang nahi kahen, hijeh chun na masanga kipah tah in kaki hkonna thu seiying kate.  
\v 11 Jerusalem'a Pathen hou dinga kahung lhun jouva pat ni som le ni jong lhing loulai ahi hi nahetdoh jeng ding ahi.  
\v 12 Eihehse ho hin Hou-In'a mitoh kakinel na jong amu naisai lou diu ahin, kikhopna in ahilou le khopi lamlhong lah a boina kasem jong amukhah lou dingu ahi.  
\v 13 Hiche mihon eihehset nau hi khat cha aphotchet na apeh theilou dingu ahi.”  
\v 14 Ahin hou dihlou lamkai ahi atiu vang chu kanom'e, ajeh chu kapu kapa teuvin ana hou Pathen chu kahou ahin, Juda te dan le themgao lekhabua kisun jouse dihtah a katahsan ahi.  
\v 15 Amaho kinepna banga keijong Pathen'in nikhat le midih le midihlou ahin kaithou kit ding ahi tia kinem kahi.  
\v 16 Hiche jeh a hi mijouse le Pathen anga dihtah a hinkho man ding kagot jing ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin kum tamtah jouvin kamite kithopina sum peding le Pathen kom'a kilhaina bol dingin Jerusalem'a kahung kilen ahileh,\x + \xo 24:17 \xt Act 21:17-28\x*  
\v 18 Hou-In sunga kauma ka kisuhtheng chu eihehse hon amu uvin, hiche pet a chu kavel'a mipi jong umlou ahin boina ima jong aumpon ahi.  
\v 19 Ahin Asia gamsunga konna Judaho mi phabep umu ahi, chule amaho chu kei hehsetna ding hola um jing'u ahi!  
\v 20 Juda te hou vaipoloi hon kachunga ipi chonsetna amu uham hiche miho hi dongin,  
\v 21 Thilkhat bouseh “thokit thudol katahsan jeh a tunia na angsung uva kachung thu kikhol ahi,” tia kasap tailou adang ima namu lou dingu ahi.\x + \xo 24:21 \xt Act 23:6\x*  
\v 22 Chuche tahsanna lampi thudol hethem tah ahitoh kilhonin, Felix chun phat asuh saobe in, “Vaipipo Lysias hung lhun kah in khongaiyun, ama ahung tengleh nathuu ngaito chen nange,” ati.  
\v 23 Chuin sepai jalamkaipa kom'a chun, “Paul chu songkul'a koiyun lang ahin aloi agol hon avila angaichat ho abolpeh theina dingun phalna peuvin,” ati.  
\v 24 Nichomkhat jouvin Felix chu ajinu Juda numei Drusilla toh ahung kit in, chuin Paul chu aga kousah lhonin Paul in Jesu Christa tahsan thudol asei chu angai lhonin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin Paul in chondihna le eima chang kitim hat chule khonunga hunglhung ding thutanna thu asei ajah phat chun Felix chu ahung kicha tan, “Tun chen lang, phat gomkom aum tengleh kahin koukit ding nahi,” tin asoldoh tan ahi.  
\v 26 Chujongleh Paul chun sum eithimpeh khante tin, akouloi loijin ahoupi jing jin ahi.  
\v 27 Chutia kumni ache jouvin, Porcius Festus in Felix panmun chu alotan, chule Felix in Juda te lung ahol jeh chun Paul chu songkul'a akhum in adalha tan ahi.   
\c 25  
\s1 Festus anga Paul thusei  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Festus in amopohna thah jop dinga Caesarea ahung lhun nithum jouvin, Jerusalem a achen ahile,  
\v 2 Hichea chun thempu pipuiho leh Judah houlamkai dang phabep in akimupi uvin Paul hehsetna thu asei tauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Festus henga chun ataouvin Paul chu Jerusalem'a ahin lesolna dingin angeh un ahi (ajeh chu lamkah a chanlhih a tha ding lung angaitou ahi).  
\v 4 Ahin Festus in adonbut na a chun, Paul chu Caesarea a kikoi ahin chule ama jeng jong khulama kilevah kit ding ahi dan aseiyin,  
\v 5 Chuin hitin aseiye, “Nangho athunei ho chu keitoh ikilhon uva, Paul in thilse abol khah le nang hon ahehset na thu nasei theiyu ahi,” ati.  
\v 6 Niget ham nisom ham jouvin Festus jong Caesarea lamah akile tan, chuin alhun lhunin ama thutanna inpia atouvin Paul chu ahenga ahin pui dingun thu apetan ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin Paul ahung lhun phat in, Jerusalem'a konna hung Judah hou lamkai ho chu ahung khomun, photchetna jong pethei louvin hehsetna khoh tah tah aseikhum tauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin Paul in ahehset nau thu lethuh nan, “Keiman Juda te dan ahin, Hou-In ahin, chule Rome te dounan themmona kaneipoi,” ati.  
\v 9 Chuin Festus in Juda te lung holnan Paul thu adongin, “Nangma Jerusalem'a chea keima angsunga amaho toh nachung chang thu khol ding nanop em?” ati.  
\v 10 Ahin Paul in adonbut in, “Kanompoi! Hiche hi Rome te thutanna mun ahin, hiche laiya hi kathu kitan ding ahi. Ajeh chu Juda te douna a kathemmo lou nahenai.  
\v 11 Chule thina ding khop themmona kanei le thi ding kada poi, ahin Caesar henga dingin kangeh joi, themmona neilou kahi le hiche miho khut a thi dingin koiman pehdohna tha ka chunga neiponte!” ati.  
\v 12 Chuin Festus in doh le sot a aneiho chengse toh akihoukhom jouvin adonbut in, “Aphai! Caesar henga nathu kisei dinga na ngeh ahitah le, Caesar henga nache ding ahitai!” ati.   
\s1 Leng Agrippa in Paul akimupi  
\p
\v 13 Nikho phabep jouvin Leng Agrippa chu asopinu Bernice toh Festus jabolna pedingin ahung lhonin,  
\v 14 Chuin nikho tampi aumkhom sungu chun Festus in Paul chung thu chu Lengpa henga chun aseiyin, “Felix in keima tan dingin mikhat songkul'a ana koiyin,  
\v 15 Jerusalem'a kaum pet chun Juda te thempu pipuiho le upahon ahehset na thu aseiyun themmonachan ding ahi eitiuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Rome te dan dungjuijin achungthu khol masa louvin mi themmo akichan theipoi kati peh e, amaho chu ahehse ho'u toh kimaitoa kidinsah a akihkonna thu kisei sahji ahi” kati.  
\v 17 “Chuin ahehse ho achungthu khola ahung phat un khongai sot louvin ajingin Paul kakou tan ahi.  
\v 18 Ahin ahehse hon aheh nau chu ka ginchat tobang themmona khatcha ana hitapon,  
\v 19 Chusang'in amaho houthu to kisai joh anahin ahi. Ajeh chu Juda ten athia ahet'u Jesu chu Paul in ahinge ati ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin keiman atanlhah je kamah jeh chun Jerusalem'a a nachung thu itan dingu ham tia kadoh le,  
\v 21 Paul in achungthu tan dingin Leng lenpa ana ngeh jotan, hijeh chun Caesar henga kasol kah a dingin songkul'a kakhume,” ati.  
\v 22 Chuin Agrippa in “ken jong kangai nome,” atin ahileh Festus in adonbut in, “Jing leh” ati peh e.  
\v 23 Chuin ajingin Agrippa le Bernice chu loupi tah in sepai vaipipo le khopi sunga milen milal ho toh thu ngaina indan sunga ahunglut un, chuin Festus in Paul chu ahin puilut dingun thu apetan ahi.  
\v 24 Chuin Festus chun, “Leng Agrippa le ahung khom mipi jouse, hiche gamsung le Jerusalem'a Juda te jousen athi dinga angeh jingu mipa chu hiche hi ahi.  
\v 25 Ahin keima lunggel in vang ima thina chan geiya ding themmona aneipoi, hijongleh aman lenglen thutanna adeisah banga, Rome a sol dinga kagel lhah ahitai.  
\v 26 Ahin lenglen pen kom'a dinga ipi kasut ding ham? Ajeh chu amona kicheh tah kahepoi. Hijeh a chu sut ding themkhat beh kahet dohna dinga tunia nangho jouse, adeh a Leng Agrippa angsunga kahin puidoh ahi.  
\v 27 Ajeh chu songkul'a konna mikhat athemmona kicheh tah umlouva lenglen kom'a sol chu angai ahipoi,” ati.   
\c 26  
\s1 Paul in aneova pat ahinkho thudol ahilchet  
\p
\v 1 Chujou chun, Agrippa in Paul jah ah, “Nakihkonna thu phong theijin nate,” ati. Hichun Paul in akhut alhaang doh in akihkonna thu aseitai.  
\v 2 “Kakipah lheh jeng e, Leng Agrippa, tunia Juda lamkai hon themmo eichen nau chung changa kakihkonna thu ja ah nang bou nahi.  
\v 3 Ajeh chu Judah te kivaipoh dol le akinel baotam nau hethem ah nahi kahen, hijeh chun ka thusei hi lungneng tah in nei ngaipeh in.”  
\v 4 Keima ka chapan laija pat a kanam mite lah le Jerusalem a kon hung seilen a, Juda nam chon le khan kichuh themsa kahi hi Juda lamkai hon ahet sohkeiyu ahi.  
\v 5 Ama hon aseinom ule, atil apat a ahet jing sau Pharisee mi, hou thudol'a chondan kikhel tah kahi aheuve.\x + \xo 26:5 \xt Act 23:6; Philp 3:5\x*  
\v 6 Chule tua hi kapu kapa teu henga Pathen tepsa hung guilhung ding kakinepna thudol'a, kachung thu khol dia hikom'a ding ah kahi.  
\v 7 Adihtah a seidin, Israel phungsom le phung nin sun le jan a anahou jingu ahi. Vo Lengpa hiche kinepna thudol'a Juda ten eiheh-u ahi bouve.  
\v 8 Ipi jeh a Pathen'in mithisa athodoh sah thei thudol hi tahsan lel nahiuvem?  
\v 9 Keima jeng jong Nazareth Jesu min douna a thil ijakai bol ding kana ngaitosa ahi.\x + \xo 26:9 \xt Act 8:3; 22:4,5\x*  
\v 10 Atahbeh in jong Jerusalem'a kana bol in, Thempu pipuiho a kon'in thuneina kalan, mitheng tampi songkul'ah kana khum in chule atha jengu jong chu pha kasan ahi.  
\v 11 Phat atamjon hou thudol'a akikhop nau intin'a jong talent kamat sah jin, Jesu atahsan nau taitom sah in hoise tah in kana douvin, gamdang miho khopi dung geijin kana nocheh jin ahi.   
\s1 Paul in ahinkho kikhel thudol avelsei  
\p
\v 12 Nikhat hi katoh ban tong jom din Thempu pipuiho thuneina le thusah kengin Damascus jonin kachen ahi.  
\v 13 Sunkim dontah in, vo Lengpa, lampia chun van'a kon nisa sanga vahjo vah khat in kei le kalhonpi ho eihin kho'uvin ahile.  
\v 14 Kabon chauvin kalhu soh tauvin ahi, hichun, Aramaic paovin kajah a, “Saul, Saul, ibola nangin nei bolset jing ham? Neidou jing hi nanga din aphat chomna aumpoi,” eiti.  
\v 15 Hichun keiman, “Nang koi nahim, Pakai?” kati. “Aman eihin donbut in, ‘nabol set jing Jesu chu kahi.  
\v 16 Tun nakeng in pansan dingin, nangma leiset kolkim vel'a kathu hettohsah le kalhacha a pang ding, chule nathil mu chengse le kahin musah kit ding chengse hettohsah a pansah dinga hung kilah kahi  
\v 17 Chule kasolna chidang namdang te lah le nanam mite lah a konna kahuhdoh jing ding nahi,  
\v 18 Amit'u hasah a, muthim lah a konna lungheiya khovah ahin mun'a thei diu le satan thaneina a konna Pathen henga ahung kiheina thei diu, chule chonset ngaidamna achan theina diu le tahsan jal a Pathen mite ahi theina diuva kasol ding nahi,’ eiti.  
\v 19 Chule, Leng Agrippa, vanlam'a kon themgao thilmu kamu thua nung ah kahi.  
\v 20 Amasan Damascus a umho henga kahil lhanglen, chujouvin Jerusalem le Juda gamkol sung chukit le chidang namdang ho hengah, chonset kisih a Pathen lam ahin belna diu le alunghei utoh lhon a thilpha abolna diuvin kahil lhanglei.\x + \xo 26:20 \xt Act 9:20,28,29\x*  
\v 21 Hiche thu kahil lhang le jeh a hi Juda hon Hou-In sunga eimat uva, tha ding eigot u ahi.  
\v 22 Ahin tuphat chana Pathen venbitna kachan jeh in mijouse, aneo kom hihen alenkom hijongleh hettohsah in kapang jing e. Thudang ima kahilpoi Themgao ho leh Mose’n hung guilhung dinga aseiyu–  
\v 23 Christan hesoh genthei athoh a, thina a konna thoudoh masapen a pang ding, chuleh Juda te le chidang namdang ho henga Pathen vah thudol aphondoh ding je kasei ahi bouve,” ati.\x + \xo 26:23 \xt 1 Crth 15:20; \xt Isa 42:6; 49:6\x*   
\s1 Agrippa tahsan na dia Paul atao  
\p
\v 24 Photlot louvin Festus chu ahung pengjah jengin, “Paul angol ah nahitai; na lekha thepnan na ngolsah ahitai,” ati.  
\v 25 Hichun Paul in adonbut in, “Angol a kahipoi, vo Lalchungnung Festus, kicheh tah a thudih kasei joh ahi bouve.  
\v 26 Chule Agrippa Lengpan jong ahei. Ijeh inem itile aning koi a kibol ahilou jeh in aman hitobang ho hi ahesoh keiye ti kichen tah in kahei, hijeh a chu hangsan tah a kasei ahi,” ati.  
\v 27 Leng Agrippa, themgao ho na tahsan em? Natahsan e ti kahei, ati.  
\v 28 Hichun Agrippa in, “Kintah a Christian hisah jeng thei dia nei gel ham?” ati.  
\v 29 Chuin Paul in adonbut in, “Gang henlang gang hih jong le, nang le hiva mipi um jouse hi, thihkhaova kakihenna ho tilouvin keima tobang hisohkei ule tin, Pathen hengah kataove,” ati.  
\v 30 Hichun Lengpa, Gamvaipo, Bernice chule adang ho se adingdoh un adalha tauve.  
\v 31 Apotdoh uva akihou nau le akinopto nau chun “Hiche mipa hin thina le songkul tanna thei chan gei ima bolset aneipoi,” atiuve.  
\v 32 Chule Agrippa in Festus jah a, “Aman Caesar henga dinga ngehna ana bollou hile lhadoh thei ahitai,” ati.   
\c 27  
\s1 Rome khopi lam jon a Paul kong'a akitol  
\p
\v 1 Chuin aphat ahung lhun phat in Italy che dingin konga katou tauvin ahi. Paul le songkul atan khompi mi phabep chu Rome sepai lamkai ho lah a Julius atiu khut a chun apedoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Chule Macedonia mi Thessalonica a konna Aristarchus jaonan, Asia gamsung sah-lhumlam a Adramyttium kong ngahmun'a kon'in konga kache tauvin ahi. Chule hiche kong chu Asia gamsung muntin'a kingapa dinga kigong ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin ajinga Sidon kong ngahmun kalhunun, Julius chun ngailut tah a Paul chu twipanga aloiho vilthei dinga phalna apeh jeh chun achen ahileh aloihon angaichat ho jouse ahin kithopi uvin ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin hichea konna twi chunga kachelai tah un huipi hattah khat in keiho lam nga-a einun den phat un kache jom thei tapouvin, hijeh chun Cyprus twikol sahlam twipi panga kache peh tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Hiti chun Cilicia le Pamphylia twipi kahopaiyun, Lycia gamsunga Myra mun'ah kaki ngauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Chuin hikom'a chun sepai jalamkai pan Alexandria a konna Egypt te kong Italy jon ding khat ahin mu phat in hiche konga chun eiheng doh tauvin ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin nikho tamtah ol olin kakitolun hahsatah in Cnidus kanai ham-ham'un, huiyin eilenan jeh un Crete twikol pang panga kakitolun, Salmone jon kajot un ahi.  
\v 8 Twi pamchin china hahsatah in kacheuvin, nahchangsalin Lasea khopi muntoh kinaicha a um Kongkai Munhoi atiu chu kalhung tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin phat tampi kamansah jouvun, konga chejom ding la aphat toh kitoh a toset toding kichat aum jeh chun, Paul in kongtol ho akimupin,  
\v 10 “Sopi te ho, iche jom uva ahile, kongkeh thei, thilkeo ho jong mangthei, chule ihinkhou jeng jong ichan theiyu ahi,” tin aseitan ahi.  
\v 11 Ahivangin songkul tangho chunga mopo lamkai pa chun, Paul thusei sangin Kong neipa le kongtol ho thusei joh chu angaiyin ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin Kongkai Munhoi chu phalbia umna dinga ahahsat jep jeh chun, konga natong ho atamjo chun Crete twipi panga Phoenix mun lhuntei ding hikom'a chu phalbi man ding adeisah un ahi. Phoenix mun chu kongkaimun nomtah ahin sah-lhum le lhang-lhum angatto ahi.  
\v 13 Chuin lhanglama kon'in hui ol olin ahung nung pan tan ahileh kongtol hon kong chethei nante tin khao alhauvin Crete vapang panga atol tauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Ahivangin chomkhat jouvin hui chedan ahung kikhelin twikhanglen'a kon'in huipi le gopi hattah (solam hui) atiu chu ahung nungin twipi langa einuh lut tauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin kongtol hon kong chu ahei joulou phat uvin, huilah a chun kong chu amoh lha tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Cauda atiu twikol neocha pang panga chun kakitol uvin anah nah in hahsatah in kongneo khat kaman ham-ham'un ahi.  
\v 17 Chuin kongtol hon hichu akhaidoh un ahunan amang un, khaovin kong noilamah akanbeh tauve; chuin ajole Syrtis kilenglut get inte ti akichauvin pondal kikhaina ho akainem uvin ahile eimoh lhoh lhoh jeng tauve.  
\v 18 Chuin huipi chun eisuh gim behseh jeh u chun ajing nikhon thil apaidoh pan tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Anithum nin amaho tah in akhuttah in kong manchah ho chu apai tauvin ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin tijat umtah huipi hattah a nikho tamtah anun a nisa le ahsi ho eisalvah u beihela aum phat chun kihing inte tia kinepna jong aum tapon ahi.  
\v 21 Chuin koima an nelouva nitamtah aum phat un Paul in mipi ho chu akoukhom un ajah uva, “Vo miho, kasei chu ngaiyuvin lang Crete chu dalhah da leuchun hitobang settona leh manthahna hi itolou dingu ahi.  
\v 22 Ahin tunjong lungneu hih un, kong hi twiya lhalut jong le koiman nahin nau nachan lou dingu ahi.  
\v 23 Ajeh chu janlhah in kahou le alhachana katoh jing ka Pathen vantil khat kahenga ahung dingin,  
\v 24 Chule hitin aseiyin ahi, kicha hih in Paul ajeh chu iti jong le nangma Caesar angsunga nadin teitei ding ahi, chule konga natoupi ho jouse toh nahoidoh sohkei dingu ahi.  
\v 25 Hijeh chun kicha hih un! Ka Pathen'in asei tobang hi ding ahi ti katahsan'e.  
\v 26 Ahin Twikol khat a vang ikongu seden tei ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Twikhanglen chunga huise  
\p
\v 27 Chuin Adria twikhanglen'a huipi hattah in eilhoh le le nau nisom le janli lhinni jankhangkimin kongtol hon kong chu tol toh akinai tai ti aging chauvin,  
\v 28 Hijeh chun twi chu ateuvin ahile feet jakhat le somni bep in athuh in, chuin chomkhat jouvin atekit-un ahile feet somko bep ahitan ahi.  
\v 29 Hiche phat chun twipanga songho kitat khading ahitai tin akichauvin, kong nunglama chun pondal li asepdoh un, ataovun khovah angah tauvin ahi.  
\v 30 Chuin kongtol ho chu kongmai lama pondal khailha ding bang akisauvin, kong chu dalhan kongneova jam ding angaito tauvin ahi.  
\v 31 Chuin Paul in Sepai jalamkaipa le asepai ho jah a “Kongtol ho kong sunga aumlou ule nangho khatcha sohcha pouvin nate,” ati.  
\v 32 Chuin Sepai hon kongneo khao chu asat tanun alha mang tauve.  
\v 33 Chuin ajing kho ahungvah phat in Paul in miho chu anne dingin asolin, “Lungkham tah a an le twi natoh khah lounau haptani ahitai.”  
\v 34 “Tun lungset tah in nangho phatchomna dingin an netauvin ajeh chu nasam'u jangkhat jeng jong mangthah louding ahi.” ati.  
\v 35 Chuin changlhah phabep alan Pathen athangvah in aheh balbal'in anetan ahi.  
\v 36 Hichun midang ho jong ahung lunglen doh un ama hon jong an anetauvin ahi.  
\v 37 Kabon chauva konga tou chu mi jani le somsagi le gup kahiuve.  
\v 38 Chuin konga touho jousen an aneh jou phat un kong chu asujaang un, asunga um suhlou chang ho chu aseplha tauvin ahi.  
\v 39 Chuin jingkah kho ahung vah phat in, aumnau vapang chu hoilai ahi ahe tapouvin ahi. Ahin twininglutna vapang khat amudoh un, ahithei le kong huhna a chu hilaimun a chu tollut ding tin angaito tauvin ahi.  
\v 40 Chuin thihhat ho alha lhauvin, twikhanglen'a adalha tauve. Chuin chuche toh thakhat in kongkhe kanna chu alham lhauvin, hui chena lama pondal atungdoh un, vapam lam chu ajon tauve.  
\v 41 Chuin twi kinong ni kisuhtona kalutkha tauvin ahile, kong manghem chu tol'a akiphut dentai. Chuin kong mailam chu long louhelin aohdentan, kong meilam chu twi kinong chun hatah in ahin sutan ahile kong chu akeh pantan ahi.  
\v 42 Chuin sepai ho chun songkul tangho chu twi aje galkaiyuva asochat louna dingun tha ding agouvin ahi.  
\v 43 Ahivangin sepai jalamkai chun Paul chu ahing hoinom jeh chun ajadan, twi japthei theiyin anajap galkai masat dingun thu apetan ahi.  
\v 44 Chule adang twijap theilou ho chu kong sunga um thingpeh ham ahilou le kongse hel hoa chu kitol dingin thu apen ahile, abonchauvin twipanga bitkeiyin asohchauvin ahi.   
\c 28  
\s1 Malta twikol mun a Paul  
\p
\v 1 Chuin ka sochat phat un, Malta twikol a um kahiu chu kahedoh tauve.  
\v 2 Hiche twikol a cheng mite chu apha lheh jengun, go ajuh a adap jeh chun, twi panga chun mei atih un eina lamtouvin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Paul in meiya tiding thing khut dimkhat ahin choiyin meichunga chun alehlut in ahile, mei asat jeh chun gul gunei khat ahung kithol doh in akhut chu achun ahi.  
\v 4 Akhut a gul akikhai den chu twikol mite chun amu uvin, khat le khat akihouvun, “Tolthat hitei ding ahi! Twipi chunga ahung sochat vanga thudih chun ahing dinga aphallou ahi,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 5 Ahin Paul in akhut a gul chu meilah a athing lhan ahile ama imacha atipon ahi.  
\v 6 Miho chun itih le ahung pomin ahilou le ahung moh lhuh dem tia angau ahi. Ahin sottah angauva ima tilouva aum chu amu phat un alunggel u akikhel tan, pathen hi ding ahi atiuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Hiche ka kingah nau twipanga chu twikol pipuipen Publius atiu chun gam anei ahin, ama chun eilem'un nithum sungin khoto tah in eivah un ahi.  
\v 8 Chutia kaum sungu chun Publius pa chu khosih le ehthit in hatah in ahung dammon ahile, Paul alut in achunga khut angamin ataopeh in ahileh ahung dam tan ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin twikol sunga damlou jouse chu ahin puiyun ahile abonun adam tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche jeh chun mihon eijabol lheh jeng tauvin, konga kache kit diu phat chun angai cha thil jousen eikithopi un ahi.   
\s1 Paul, Rome khopi mun alhun  
\p
\v 11 Chuin kongke jouva pat lhathum jou phalbi laitah in, pathen lim alu ni neiya kisem Alexandria konga chun kakitol kit tauvin ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin Syracuse mun'a ka kingapa uvin nithum kaki bangpa uvin ahi.  
\v 13 Hichea pat chun Rhegium lama kakitol kit un ahile, nikhat jouvin lhanglam hui hattah in ahung nungin hichun ajingin Puteuli mun kalhung tauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Hichelai mun a chun seijui ho ana umun, ama hon eikouvun hapta khat lam kaum khomun, chujouvin Rome kajon tauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin Rome a um sopi hon keiho kacheu thu ajah phat un Appian a mipi kikhopna mun a eihung kimupi uvin ahi. Chuleh adang hon jinlhun in thum'a eihung lhunpi uvin ahi. Hichu Paul in amu phat in akitilkhou lheh jengin Pathen athangvah in ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Rome kalhun phat uvin, Paul chu achangin inchom khat ah aumsah un sepai ho angasah un ahi.   
\s1 Rome mun a Paul  
\p
\v 17 Rome alhunkal nithum jouvin Paul in amun a Judah te lamkai ho chu akou khomin, “Sopi te ho, Jerusalem'a eimanun, eiho mite leh ipu ipa teu chonna dan ima kasuhkhel lou vang'in Rome mite khut a eipedoh un ahi.  
\v 18 Rome ten kachung thu akholun thina chan gei ding themmona ima amudoh lou jeh un lhadoh dingin eigong un ahi.  
\v 19 Ahin hiche thulhuhna chu Judah vaipo hon adoudalun ahi, hijeh a chu kamite themmo chansah nom hih jonglehng Caesar in kachung thu atan ding chu ngaikhoh kasah ahitai.\x + \xo 28:19 \xt Act 25:11\x*  
\v 20 Tunia nangho kahin koukhom lona chu ikihoulim khom uva, chule Israel te kinepna Messiah chu ahung tai, ti katahsan jeh a kihen kahina thu kahil chen nomu ahi,” ati.  
\v 21 Chuin ama hon adonbut un “Judea gam'a kon'in lekhathot kamu pouvin, chule ahung ho lah a kon'in jong nangma hehsetna thu ima kaja pouve.  
\v 22 Ahin keihon jong na tahsan thudol chu ka hetchen nom uve ajeh chu hiche thudol kiseina mun jousea aki seisetna thu bou kaja jiuve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin phat akitemun, aphat tep nikhou chun mi tamtah Paul umna'a chun ahung khom uvin ahi. Chuin Paul in Pathen Lenggam thu ahilin miho tamtah chu Pathen Lekhabua kon'in Jesu thudol ah ajoltan ahi. Hiti chun jingkah a pat nilhah geiyin Mose danthu le themgao lekhabua kon'in ahoulim in ahi.   
\p
\v 24 Chuin mi phabep in athuhil chu ajop un, konkhat in atahsan pouvin ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin amaho le amaho suhnel tounel akitho jouvun hiche thu hi Paul kom'a kon'in achainan angaiyun ache tauvin ahi. Hiche athu ngaiyu chu hiche hi ahi: “Lhagao Theng in napu'u Isaiah henga ana phondoh thu chu adih ahi.  
\v 26 ‘Hiche mite kom'a khun chen lang gasei tan, ka thusei hi najah tengule ipi kiseina ham nahet lou dingu, kathilbol namu tengule ipi kabol nahet theilou dingu ahi.\x + \xo 28:26 \xt Isa 6:9,10\x*  
\v 27 Ajeh chu hiche mite lungthim hi atah dentan, chule anakol uvin kho ajapon, chule amit u asing tauvin ahi. Hijeh a chu amit uvin amuthei hih a, chule anakol uvin ajah theilou, chule alungthim uvin jong ahethem thei hih un, keima suhdam dingin jong kahenga ahung kihei thei tapouve,’  
\v 28 Hijeh chun hiche thu hi nang hon jong nahet diu kadei ahi, Pathen'a konna huhhingna thu hi chidang namdang te henga jong kipe ahin chule ama hon jong asan u ahitai,” ati.  
\v 29 Aman hiche thu ho aseijou chun, Juda hon adalhauvin, chule amaho le amaho akihanel lheh jeng tauve.  
\v 30 Chujou kumni sung chun Paul in ama sumin insan man akipeh in Rome ah achengin ama vil'a che jouse chu ana lemin,  
\v 31 Chuti chun hangsan tah in Pathen Lenggam thudol asam phonglen, chule Pakai Jesu Christa thudol chu ahil len koima chan ana kham tang joupon ahi.   